Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-= 圣城家园 CnSCG 荣誉出品 =-\N南宫长风 作品\N{\rEng}hd.cnscg.com
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.95,0:00:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,全世界的青年男女\N{\rEng}Young people from all over the globe...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.86,0:00:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,为全人类的未来奋战\N{\rEng}are joining up to fight for the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.03,0:00:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我要出力 - 我要出力\N{\rEng}- I'm doing my part. - I'm doing my part.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.95,0:00:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我要出力 - 我也要出力\N{\rEng}- I'm doing my part. - I'm doing my part too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他们全在出力 你呢？\N{\rEng}They're doing their part, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.75,0:00:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,加入机动部队 拯救世界\N{\rEng}Join the Mobile Infantry and save the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.34,0:00:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,入伍就能获得公民权\N{\rEng}Service guarantees citizenship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.87,0:00:58.74,Chs,,0,0,0,,“你想知道更多吗？”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.13,0:01:00.05,Chs,,0,0,0,,“虫族陨石”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,虫族陨石再度侵犯地球\N{\rEng}The bugs send another meteor our way...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.89,0:01:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这次我们有所准备\N{\rEng}but this time we're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.77,0:01:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,地球的防卫日益精良\N{\rEng}Planetary defences are better than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.28,0:01:13.86,Chs,,0,0,0,,“你想知道更多吗？”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.86,0:01:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,虫族陨石来自克兰达夫星球\N{\rEng}Klendathu, source of the bug meteor attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.53,0:01:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,环绕着双子星系统运行\N{\rEng}orbits a twin star system whose brutal gravitational forces...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.03,0:01:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,附近的带状行星群带来\N{\rEng}produce an unlimited supply of bug meteorites...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.16,0:01:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,大量的虫族陨石\N{\rEng}in the form of this asteroid belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.87,0:01:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,为了捍卫太阳系\N{\rEng}To ensure the safety of our solar system...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.21,0:01:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,必须消灭克兰达夫星球\N{\rEng}Klendathu must be eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.21,0:01:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,现在从克兰达夫星球现场\N{\rEng}We break net now and take you live to Klendathu...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.05,0:01:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,转播这场大战\N{\rEng}where the invasion has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.88,0:01:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,卫星连线 2…1…开始\N{\rEng}EXQ uplink on two, one. You're on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.39,0:01:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们刚降落在… - 快 快 快！\N{\rEng}- We'vejust landed here on what cap troopers... - Move, move, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.05,0:01:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 被称为大K星的战场 - 快！ 走！ 走！\N{\rEng}- are calling Big K, - Come on! Move, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.22,0:01:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 第六机动部队正展开攻击 - 快！\N{\rEng}- with the 6th Mobile Infantry Division! - Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.89,0:01:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这丑陋的星球全是大虫\N{\rEng}It's an ugly planet, a bug planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.23,0:01:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,威胁人类的生存\N{\rEng}A planet hostile to life as we know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:01:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,救命啊！\N{\rEng}Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.83,0:02:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快走 快 快 - 快！\N{\rEng}- Come on! Go, go, go! - Keep moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.71,0:02:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,快离开这里\N{\rEng}Get out of here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.72,0:02:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,基顿 不！\N{\rEng}Kitten, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.25,0:02:49.22,Chs,,0,0,0,,“一年前”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.58,0:03:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞哥…瑞哥…瑞哥！\N{\rEng}Rico. Rico. Rico!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,专心点\N{\rEng}Pay attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.43,0:03:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 瑞斯加科先生\N{\rEng}Sorry, Mr Rasczak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.47,0:03:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,总而言之\N{\rEng}Let's sum up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.60,0:03:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,今年我们谈过民主制度失败的原因\N{\rEng}This year we explored the failure of democracy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.48,0:03:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 坏家伙 - 社会学家…\N{\rEng}- Bad boy. - how the social scientists brought our world...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.35,0:03:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,让世界陷入混乱\N{\rEng}to the brink of chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.27,0:03:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们谈到退伍军人终于接管统治…\N{\rEng}We talked about the veterans, how they took control...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,长久以来使得地球得以安定\N{\rEng}and imposed the stability that has lasted for generations since.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这些是事实让你们学到了什么？\N{\rEng}You know these facts...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我问你为何只有公民才能投票？\N{\rEng}but have I taught you anything of value this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你 为什么只有公民才有投票权？\N{\rEng}You. Why are only citizens allowed to vote?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.45,0:03:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一种奖赏\N{\rEng}It's a reward,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.04,0:03:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那是为联邦政府服务得到的奖励\N{\rEng}what the Federation gives you for doing Federal Service.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不对 不对\N{\rEng}No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,赐与的权利没有价值\N{\rEng}Something given has no value.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.71,0:03:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,投票权是政治权\N{\rEng}Look, when you vote, you are exercising political authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.09,0:03:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是力量 力量就是暴力\N{\rEng}You're using force. And force, my friends, is violence,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.14,0:03:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,暴力是所有权力的来源\N{\rEng}the supreme authority from which all other authority is derived.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈妈说暴力解决不了问题\N{\rEng}Uh, my mother always said violence never solves anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.23,0:03:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,真的？\N{\rEng}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.81,0:04:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我真好奇广岛之父会不会这么说\N{\rEng}I wonder what the city fathers of Hiroshima would say about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你\N{\rEng}You.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.28,0:04:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,大概不会这么说 因为广岛被炸了\N{\rEng}They probably wouldn't say anything. Hiroshima was destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\rEng}Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,历史证明赤裸裸的…\N{\rEng}Naked force has resolved more issues...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,暴力解决许多问题\N{\rEng}throughout history than any other factor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.54,0:04:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,暴力解决不了问题的论调…\N{\rEng}The contrary opinion, that violence never solves anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.08,0:04:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,…只是自欺欺人的想法\N{\rEng}is wishful thinking at its worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.46,0:04:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,忘记历史教训的人将付出代价\N{\rEng}People who forget that always pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.71,0:04:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞哥 在道德上…\N{\rEng}Rico, what's the moral difference, if any...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.38,0:04:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,公民和平民有何不同？\N{\rEng}between a civilian and a citizen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.43,0:04:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,公民接受政府赋与的责任…\N{\rEng}A citizen accepts personal responsibility for the safety...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,并且誓死捍卫地球\N{\rEng}of the body politic, defending it with his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.93,0:04:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 平民则不然 - 标准答案\N{\rEng}- A civilian does not. - The exact words of the text.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,可是你了解吗？ 你相信吗？\N{\rEng}But do you understand it? Do you believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.19,0:04:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不知道 - 那是当然的\N{\rEng}- I don't know. - Of course you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.24,0:04:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是死到临头\N{\rEng}I doubt anyone here would recognize civic virtue...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.41,0:04:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都不了解公民的责任 第三节下课 第四节五分钟后上课\N{\rEng}if it reached up and bit you in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,别在这里\N{\rEng}Not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 咱们去看数学课的成绩\N{\rEng}Come on, let's see if they posted the math final.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 瑞哥 赢得了泰斯拉队吗？ - 我们会痛宰他们\N{\rEng}- Rico, we gonna take Tesla? - We're gonna kill 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,记住 毕业生都得填写710表格\N{\rEng}Remember, all graduating seniors must fill out a 710 form.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,星舰军校最重视数学成绩\N{\rEng}First thing Fleet Academy looks at is your math scores.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,祝我好运\N{\rEng}Wish me luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:33.66,Chs,,0,0,0,,“艾邦妮兹 数学97%”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 要走了 - 干得好\N{\rEng}- Way to go. - Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,该你了 等一下\N{\rEng}Your turn. Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我去找马可 他姐姐在星际舰队\N{\rEng}I want to talk to Marco. His sister's at Fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 马可 - 嗨 卡门\N{\rEng}- Marco. - Hi, Carmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.63,0:05:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你姐有消息吗？ - 她当上飞行员\N{\rEng}- What do you hear about Roxy? - She made pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.73,0:05:49.23,Chs,,0,0,0,,“瑞哥 数学35%”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,35% 真棒\N{\rEng}Thirty-five percent. Very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.51,0:05:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,大伙看 35%\N{\rEng}Look at that. Thirty-five percent, ladies and gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:05:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,分数真高\N{\rEng}Big numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.64,0:06:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 卡尔 - 抱歉\N{\rEng}- Carl. - Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你们还没上床吧 别骗我\N{\rEng}So, you haven't done it yet, have you? Don't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.15,0:06:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不急\N{\rEng}I'm not in any hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.28,0:06:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有人在等你 - 那么？\N{\rEng}- Others are waiting. - And?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你能猜到她在想什么？ - 不必猜\N{\rEng}- Did you read her mind? - Don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.45,0:06:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,她在想什么很明显\N{\rEng}It's pretty clear what she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀 我要的是卡门\N{\rEng}Yeah, but I want Carmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.29,0:06:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你想得要死 - 再见 马可\N{\rEng}- Aw, you got it bad. - Bye, Marco.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,别忘了下午的事\N{\rEng}Hey, don't forget about this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他老是为了亲你芳泽耽误正事\N{\rEng}He's always late when he walks you home to fish for a kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,快走开\N{\rEng}Get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 马可的姐姐当上飞行员 - 你也会的\N{\rEng}- Marco's sister made pilot. - So will you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.10,0:06:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,想想看 如果要驾驶五十万吨重的星际战舰\N{\rEng}I mean, imagine flying a half a million tons of starship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你就得勇气十足\N{\rEng}You gotta have nerves of steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 你有没有种呢？\N{\rEng}Yeah, you do. Let's see how yours hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,开始吧\N{\rEng}You may begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:06:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是一只虫 戴上护镜\N{\rEng}Aw, come on, it's just a bug. You better put your goggles on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,只是一只虫？\N{\rEng}"Just a bug."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.54,0:07:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,人类自以为是大自然主宰者\N{\rEng}We humans like to think we are nature's finest achievement.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.67,0:07:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,其实并不然\N{\rEng}I'm afraid it just isn't true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.00,0:07:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这只甲虫远比人类优良\N{\rEng}This Arkellian sand beetle is superior in many ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.55,0:07:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,它的繁殖力很强 没有私心…\N{\rEng}It reproduces in vast numbers, has no ego...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不会恐惧 绝不怕死\N{\rEng}has no fear, doesn't now about death...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.48,0:07:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,它是虫族社会完美的一份子\N{\rEng}and so is the perfect selfless member of society.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,人类创造了艺术数学…\N{\rEng}But humans have created art, mathematics...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.02,0:07:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,和星际旅行\N{\rEng}and interstellar travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.73,0:07:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 不过千万别自大\N{\rEng}True. But before you let that go to your head...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,就拿阿瑞克尼虫族来说\N{\rEng}take the example of the Arachnids...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.24,0:07:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那是高度进化的社会\N{\rEng}a highly evolved insect society.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,以人类的标准来说它们的智慧很低\N{\rEng}By human standards, they are relatively stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,它们却有数百万年的进化史\N{\rEng}but their evolution stretches over millions of years...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 现在 - 这儿 拿着\N{\rEng}- and now... - Here, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,它们能够把胚种\N{\rEng}they can colonize planets...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.88,0:07:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,送入太空占领别的星球\N{\rEng}by hurling their spore into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.88,0:07:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,应该找到了\N{\rEng}Okay, I think we got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:07:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这是心脏\N{\rEng}That's the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.22,0:08:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这是胃囊\N{\rEng}And here's the stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.81,0:08:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这算勇气十足？\N{\rEng}Nerves of steel, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.40,0:08:13.74,Chs,,0,0,0,,“不符合”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,别费力去想 凭你的直觉想像画面\N{\rEng}Don't think about it. Just go on instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,试着将它形象化\N{\rEng}Try to visualize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到黑桃A\N{\rEng}I see the ace of spades.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.69,0:08:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,统计学上的概率\N{\rEng}You know, statistically speaking,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道就算瞎猜 到现在也该猜中了吧！ ！\N{\rEng}you should have accidentally guessed right by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 再试一次 - 我不会心灵感应 而且运气也很背\N{\rEng}- Try another. - So my psychic abilities are zero and I'm unlucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这跟运气无关\N{\rEng}No, luck's not a factor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.99,0:08:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,有些人就是特别灵敏\N{\rEng}No one really knows why some people are sensitive and some aren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道？ 也许这是人类下一步的进化\N{\rEng}Who knows? Maybe it's a new stage of human evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:09:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才有这种研究\N{\rEng}That's why they do these kind of Federal studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,西哈诺 该死 暂停\N{\rEng}What... Cyrano... Oh, shit. Time out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.21,0:09:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,它只是不甘寂寞\N{\rEng}Oh, he just wants some attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.67,0:09:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你从不陪它玩\N{\rEng}You don't play with him any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.38,0:09:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,西哈诺…\N{\rEng}Cyrano.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,去烦我老妈去\N{\rEng}Go bug Mom, Cyrano.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.40,0:09:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎么做的？\N{\rEng}How do you make him do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我让它觉得我妈脚上有食物\N{\rEng}Oh, I gave him the impression there's a grub crawling up my mom's leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,它非吃到不可\N{\rEng}He's on a mission to go eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,滚开 别碰我\N{\rEng}Ow! Oh! Get out! Get off my leg! Oh! Carl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好别在我身上用心灵感应这招\N{\rEng}I sure hope you don't do anything like that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.79,0:09:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,别怕 对人类我没辙…暂时不行\N{\rEng}Don't be afraid. Can't do human. Yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.84,0:09:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\rEng}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好！\N{\rEng}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.23,0:10:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好啊！ - 老虎队得分\N{\rEng}- Yeah! Yeah! - Touchdown Tigers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.11,0:10:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的比数是41比38\N{\rEng}And the score is now 4 1-38.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.61,0:10:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,老虎队领先 只胜两局\N{\rEng}Tigers lead with 2.:46 remaining...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是布宜诺斯艾利斯球场\N{\rEng}here at the Buenos Aires Sports Arena.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.03,0:10:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,巨人队喊暂停\N{\rEng}Time out Giants.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.53,0:10:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你还好吧？ - 好多了\N{\rEng}- Are you all right? - Much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 现在 - 好\N{\rEng}- Now. - Good.Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好 上啊！\N{\rEng}All right! Way to go, team!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.37,0:10:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 你的头盔\N{\rEng}Hey! Your helmet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,球赛后你要干嘛？\N{\rEng}So, what are you doing after the game?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都要参加舞会 你去吗？\N{\rEng}Well, everyone's going to the dance, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不清楚 今晚是我当平民的最后一夜\N{\rEng}I don't know. It's my last night as a civilian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 上 12号！ 冲！ - 明天我就要去特雷斯卡瓦\N{\rEng}- Come on, number 12! Let's go! - Ship out for Tereshkova tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.97,0:10:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你要去星舰军校？ - 嗯\N{\rEng}- You're going to the Fleet Academy? - Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.77,0:10:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想去\N{\rEng}That's where I want to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.23,0:10:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,十二号 上场了\N{\rEng}Come on, number 12! Let's play ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.94,0:10:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,别打我女友的主意\N{\rEng}Don't get any ideas about my girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,情场如战场\N{\rEng}All is fair in love and war.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.61,0:10:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 巨人队！ 巨人队！ - 强尼 加油\N{\rEng}- Giants! Giants! - Johnny! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.42,0:11:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 好啊！\N{\rEng}Hey, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.13,0:11:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,巨人队以43分领先 离终场只剩4秒钟\N{\rEng}Giants leading 43-4 1. Just over 4 2 seconds remaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.72,0:11:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,老虎队的时间所剩不多\N{\rEng}- Yeah! - All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.10,0:11:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,艾文 拉森 挡住攻击\N{\rEng}Irvin, Lathom, cover the rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.10,0:11:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,派瑞做假动作 勃迪跑远点\N{\rEng}Perry, fake left. Bertolli, you go long.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.19,0:11:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞哥 翻跳动作 懂吗？\N{\rEng}Rico, flip six three hole. Got it? Hey, Rico?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.65,0:11:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿！ - 什么？\N{\rEng}- Hey! - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.11,0:11:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,专心点 翻跳动作 懂吗？\N{\rEng}You're drifting! Flip six, three hole, on one! Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 尽管把球传给我 蒂丝 - 准备好了？\N{\rEng}- Just throw me the ball, Diz. - Ready? Break!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好！ 走 走！\N{\rEng}Yeah! Go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好！\N{\rEng}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.48,0:12:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,耶！\N{\rEng}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.82,0:12:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,得分了 比赛结束\N{\rEng}He's in there. It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.42,0:12:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你一下子就长这么大了\N{\rEng}Who said you could grow up so fast, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.80,0:12:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,妈 别这样\N{\rEng}Mom, don't get mushy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这是今天寄来的\N{\rEng}This came for you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.89,0:12:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是你要的吧？\N{\rEng}I presume, at your request.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.52,0:12:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我有很多朋友都要服役\N{\rEng}A lot of my friends are doing Federal Service.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.73,0:12:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是想报名入伍吧？\N{\rEng}Well, you're not thinking of applying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.27,0:12:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你疯啦？\N{\rEng}Have you lost your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我就算是要挨鞭刑也不准你去自毁前程\N{\rEng}I'd rather take ten lashes in Public Square than see you ruin your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这是志愿服役\N{\rEng}It's a term of service.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.03,0:12:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不是从军\N{\rEng}It's not a career.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:13:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想一个人出去…\N{\rEng}I just want to get out on my own...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,见识一下银河系风光\N{\rEng}see the galaxy for a couple years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,强尼 当兵会死人的\N{\rEng}Johnny, people get killed in the Federal Service.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.71,0:13:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁把你说动的？ 是那个老师 对吧？\N{\rEng}Who gave you this idea? It's that teacher, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫什么？ 你应该知道\N{\rEng}What's his name? You know the one I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.55,0:13:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 瑞斯加科先生 - 瑞斯加科？\N{\rEng}- Mr Rasczak. - Rasczak?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.72,0:13:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这名字真可笑 法律应该…\N{\rEng}Silly name. There should be a law against...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,禁止学校召募新兵\N{\rEng}using a school as a recruiting station.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞斯加科不会这么做\N{\rEng}No, Rasczak doesn't do that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,其实他反对学生从军\N{\rEng}He sort of discourages you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.94,0:13:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好\N{\rEng}Well, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.82,0:13:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你得上哈佛 没什么好说的\N{\rEng}'Cause you're going to Harvard, and that's the end of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.94,0:13:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的决定 不是你的\N{\rEng}It's my decision, not yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.53,0:13:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是这样吗？ - 别吵了\N{\rEng}- Oh, is that how it is, huh? - Wait, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.24,0:13:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你父亲要给你个惊喜\N{\rEng}Uh, Dad and I have a surprise for you that will settle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.79,0:13:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你猜得到吗？\N{\rEng}Can you guess what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,猜不到\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.83,0:13:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你想见识银河系风光\N{\rEng}You wanted to see the galaxy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.84,0:13:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,到土星外环旅行如何？\N{\rEng}How about a trip to the Outer Rings?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:13:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,西格玛海滩\N{\rEng}Zegema Beach. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.39,0:14:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直想去那儿\N{\rEng}I've always wanted to go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.05,0:14:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 就这么说定了\N{\rEng}Good, good. Then it's all settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.62,0:14:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,别走开\N{\rEng}Sure. Don't go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我想找瑞斯加科先生\N{\rEng}I'm just gonna go see Mr Rasczak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞哥 想跳舞吗？\N{\rEng}Hey, Rico, do you want to dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂丝 我答应卡门\N{\rEng}Actually, Diz, I promised Carmen...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.79,0:14:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,真可惜 她不在\N{\rEng}Aw, come on. Too bad for her if she's not around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.51,0:14:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,过了今晚…\N{\rEng}You know, it's sad. After tonight, most of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.34,0:14:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们恐怕不会再见面\N{\rEng}probably won't see each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你要替巴西队打球吗？\N{\rEng}So, you still gonna play for Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.94,0:14:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀 除非东京队要征召我\N{\rEng}Yeah, looks like. Unless Tokyo lets me start.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.48,0:14:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,谁抢到你就走运\N{\rEng}Well, anyone who gets you is lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.11,0:15:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们怎么没成为一对？\N{\rEng}Johnny, how come we never got together?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.78,0:15:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能只当朋友吗？\N{\rEng}Can't we just be friends, Diz?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.45,0:15:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rEng}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.54,0:15:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢 - 晚上好\N{\rEng}- Thank you. - Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂丝 我想找瑞斯加科先生\N{\rEng}Look, Diz, I want to talk to Mr Rasczak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.67,0:15:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好赶快去\N{\rEng}Well, you better hurry up if you want to catch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.18,0:15:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你对我最好\N{\rEng}You're the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞斯加科先生\N{\rEng}Mr Rasczak!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么事？ 瑞哥 - 我要谢谢你\N{\rEng}- What is it, Rico? - I want to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我最喜欢你的课\N{\rEng}Your class was the best one I had this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.07,0:15:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我只希望你能有所收获\N{\rEng}Well, it's really not my job to please. I just hope you learned something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.74,0:15:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我想入伍\N{\rEng}Well, I want to join up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我有成为公民的勇气\N{\rEng}I think I got what it takes to be a citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.58,0:15:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 去试吧\N{\rEng}Good for you. Go find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.04,0:15:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的决定我父母却反对\N{\rEng}Well, my parents are against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:15:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这是我的选择\N{\rEng}And I know it's my choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.71,0:16:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想…\N{\rEng}I was wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.59,0:16:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你若是我 你会怎么做？\N{\rEng}what would you do if you were me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.05,0:16:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,能决定自己的前程\N{\rEng}Figuring things out for yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.43,0:16:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,才是真正的自由\N{\rEng}is the only freedom anyone really has.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,珍惜这自由\N{\rEng}Use that freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.26,0:16:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,自己决定吧\N{\rEng}Make up your own mind, Rico.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.25,0:16:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,别乱讲\N{\rEng}Don't exaggerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的 你的眼睛好美\N{\rEng}I'm serious. I think you have really beautiful eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你了解？ - 强尼\N{\rEng}- You know? - Johnny.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这是山德\N{\rEng}Uh, this is Zander.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.76,0:16:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在球场上较过劲\N{\rEng}Yeah, we know each other from the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.59,0:16:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你不介意吧？ - 不介意 我们赢了\N{\rEng}- No hard feelings? - No, none at all. We won.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 卡门 最后一支舞\N{\rEng}Come on, Carmen. It's the last dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.44,0:16:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我在军校会见到你\N{\rEng}Well, maybe I'll see you at the Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:16:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 也许会吧\N{\rEng}Yeah. Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.11,0:17:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 祝你好运 - 山德也要当飞行员\N{\rEng}- Good luck. - Zander's going for pilot too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你们真是绝配 卡门\N{\rEng}You two have so much in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.62,0:17:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,强尼·瑞哥 你在吃醋吗？\N{\rEng}Johnny Rico, are you jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.79,0:17:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,也许吧\N{\rEng}Well, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.54,0:17:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你不必吃醋\N{\rEng}You don't have to be jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.05,0:17:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 嗨…快分开 你们两个\N{\rEng}Hey, hey, break it up, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要亲热就到别的地方\N{\rEng}There's a place for that sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.22,0:17:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我考虑好了 我要入伍\N{\rEng}I've been thinking, and I'm gonna do it, Carmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.06,0:17:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我要加入联邦军队\N{\rEng}I'm gonna go for Federal Service.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.02,0:17:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\rEng}That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我和卡尔明天登记 和我们一起去吧\N{\rEng}Carl and I are signing up tomorrow. Come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我会的\N{\rEng}I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.57,0:17:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我父亲今晚不在家\N{\rEng}My father's not home tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.18,0:18:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我了解从军的…\N{\rEng}I do now, of my own free will...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.85,0:18:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,意义和义务\N{\rEng}after having been duly advised and warned...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.35,0:18:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这一切完全出于自愿\N{\rEng}of the meaning and consequences of this oath...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.69,0:18:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我至少\N{\rEng}enrol in the Federal Service...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,必须服役两年\N{\rEng}for not less than two years...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.36,0:18:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,若是有需要…\N{\rEng}and as much longer as may be required...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.53,0:18:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿继续效忠部队\N{\rEng}by the needs of the Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.82,0:18:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 完了？ - 谢谢\N{\rEng}- All set? - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.08,0:18:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,又来一批新兵\N{\rEng}Fresh meat for the grinder, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.29,0:18:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你们的成绩如何？ - 我要当飞行员\N{\rEng}- So, how'd you kids do? - I'm gonna be a pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 我们很需要飞行员\N{\rEng}Well, good for you. We need all the pilots we can get.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.97,0:18:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你被分派到研发部门吗？ - 没有\N{\rEng}- Hey, did you get starside R and D? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.93,0:19:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不是吧？ - 我要到战略理论部\N{\rEng}- I don't believe it. - I got Games and Theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.52,0:19:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,战略理论？\N{\rEng}Games and Theory?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那是军事情报部 - 嗯\N{\rEng}- That's military intelligence. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好家伙 卡尔\N{\rEng}Way to go, Carl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.65,0:19:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,下次见面我就得向你敬礼\N{\rEng}Next time we meet, I'll probably have to salute you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.44,0:19:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\rEng}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.28,0:19:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢 孩子？\N{\rEng}How about you, son?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 机动部队 长官 - 很好\N{\rEng}- Infantry, sir. - Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.29,0:19:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,机动部队让我成为现在这样的男子汉\N{\rEng}Mobile Infantry made me the man I am today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.54,0:19:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,新兵必须在二十四小时内…\N{\rEng}All recruits must report to the Federal Transportation Hub...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.29,0:19:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,到联邦运送站报到\N{\rEng}within 2 4 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎加入联邦军队的行列\N{\rEng}Welcome to the adventure of Federal Service.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.71,0:19:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们一起发誓\N{\rEng}Let's make a vow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.09,0:19:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎样 我们永远是朋友\N{\rEng}No matter what, we'll always be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.26,0:19:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我同意\N{\rEng}I'll go for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.14,0:19:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们恐怕不会再见面\N{\rEng}Well, chances are we'll never see each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.23,0:19:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,分隔几百万光年的距离\N{\rEng}We'll be millions of light-years away from each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.40,0:19:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 好呀 有何不可？\N{\rEng}But, uh, yeah, sure. Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你给我去办退役\N{\rEng}You'll resign, and that's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.45,0:19:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然很没面子 不过也只能这样了\N{\rEng}It may look bad, but if that's the worst you suffer, then that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.41,0:20:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不要退役 - 你一定要\N{\rEng}- I won't quit! - I'm telling you, you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.41,0:20:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能入伍 你要去渡假\N{\rEng}You're not going back. You're going on vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我不去渡假\N{\rEng}I am not going on vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.58,0:20:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我要当公民\N{\rEng}I want to be a citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.46,0:20:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的决定\N{\rEng}It's my decision. I made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.00,0:20:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你走出去找就不认你这儿子\N{\rEng}You walk out that door, you are cut off, young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.00,0:20:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,懂吗？\N{\rEng}You understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.67,0:20:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我不要你了\N{\rEng}All right, that's it! You are cut off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.18,0:20:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是何必呢？\N{\rEng}Johnny, why won't you change your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.18,0:20:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,当公民这么重要吗？\N{\rEng}Does citizenship mean that much to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.18,0:20:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,当然重要\N{\rEng}Well, yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.39,0:20:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,希望如此\N{\rEng}Well, I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你别为了穿帅制服的…\N{\rEng}I hope you don't ruin your life over some silly little girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.02,0:20:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,女孩而自毁前程\N{\rEng}who wants to look handsome in a uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.06,0:20:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别这么说卡门 - 强尼\N{\rEng}- Don't talk about Carmen that way! - Johnny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.86,0:20:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,听到什么吗？\N{\rEng}Do you have everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.62,0:20:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rEng}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.04,0:20:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,强尼\N{\rEng}Johnny
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.50,0:20:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你迟到了 - 我父亲帮我收拾行李\N{\rEng}- You're late. - My dad had to help me pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:20:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他怕再也见不到我\N{\rEng}Suddenly he's afraid he's never gonna see me again or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.13,0:20:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他真好 不过很费时间\N{\rEng}It was sweet, but it took forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.72,0:21:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜我准备好了\N{\rEng}Oh. Anyway, I guess I'm ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.56,0:21:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是 我只剩这身衣服\N{\rEng}Yeah, me too. I'm wearing everything I own.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.40,0:21:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我很遗憾你的父母反对\N{\rEng}I'm sorry your parents were mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.40,0:21:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,管它呢 反正…\N{\rEng}Who cares? The Federation will give me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.86,0:21:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这两年军队会养我 对吧？\N{\rEng}everything I need for the next two years, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.78,0:21:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你和卡尔联络过吗？ - 有 他早上就走了\N{\rEng}- You talk to Carl? - Yeah, he left this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.58,0:21:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他不能说去哪里 - 能够入伍我好兴奋\N{\rEng}- Couldn't say where. - Oh, it's exciting, going away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.50,0:21:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我也很害怕 你不会吗？\N{\rEng}But I'm scared. Aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.25,0:21:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我会很想你\N{\rEng}I'm gonna miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.59,0:21:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我也会想你\N{\rEng}I'm gonna miss you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.76,0:21:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\rEng}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.93,0:21:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,前往特雷斯卡瓦的新兵准备启程\N{\rEng}Outbound group 94B to Tereshkova...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.10,0:21:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我该走了\N{\rEng}That's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.23,0:21:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,说一次 试试看\N{\rEng}Just say it once. Try it on for size.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.86,0:21:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\rEng}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.83,0:22:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,别忘了写信给我\N{\rEng}Don't forget to write.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.04,0:22:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会忘的\N{\rEng}I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.05,0:22:23.69,Chs,,0,0,0,,“联邦电视网”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.95,0:22:25.72,Chs,,0,0,0,,“世界团结一致”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.72,0:22:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,全自动步枪 谁想拿？\N{\rEng}Fully automatic Morita. Who wants to hold it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.39,0:22:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我！ 我！ 我…\N{\rEng}Me! Me! Me! Me! Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.73,0:22:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,公民万岁 人民创造美好明天\N{\rEng}Citizen rule. People making a better tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.81,0:22:42.14,Chs,,0,0,0,,“你想知道更多吗？”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.32,0:22:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,杀人犯今天被捕后接受审判\N{\rEng}A murderer was captured this morning and tried today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.45,0:22:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,有罪\N{\rEng}Guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.70,0:22:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,处以死刑\N{\rEng}Sentence.: death.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.46,0:22:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚六点行刑 实况转播\N{\rEng}Execution tonight at 6.:00. All net. All channels.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.18,0:22:55.82,Chs,,0,0,0,,你想知道更多吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.03,0:22:59.40,Chs,,0,0,0,,“你能心灵感应吗？”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.80,0:23:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你觉得能\N{\rEng}If you think you're psychic,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.80,0:23:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,也许是真的\N{\rEng}maybe you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.31,0:23:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,各地都在进行这项研究\N{\rEng}Federal studies are being conducted in your community.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.16,0:23:14.18,Chs,,0,0,0,,你想知道更多吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.73,0:23:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,每个小学生都知道阿瑞克尼虫很危险\N{\rEng}Every school kid knows that Arachnids are dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.35,0:23:24.32,Chs,,0,0,0,,“不宜观赏”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.32,0:23:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,摩门教徒却罔顾联邦警告\N{\rEng}However, Mormon extremists disregarded Federal warnings...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.41,0:23:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,在虫族隔离区建立教会\N{\rEng}and established Fort Joe Smith deep inside the Arachnid Quarantine Zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.75,0:23:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不料该地区早就被别人占领\N{\rEng}Too late, they realized that Dantana had already been chosen by other colonists.:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.00,0:23:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,阿瑞克尼虫族\N{\rEng}Arachnids.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.42,0:23:40.42,Chs,,0,0,0,,你想知道更多吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.01,0:23:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一 二 三 四！ - 你们大半都…\N{\rEng}- One, two, three, four! - Most of you will not...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.10,0:23:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,熬不过魔鬼训练\N{\rEng}live to be in the Mobile Infantry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.89,0:23:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你们都不够强\N{\rEng}The trouble is, you are not good enough the way you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.65,0:23:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,手放好\N{\rEng}Hands at your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.86,0:23:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,抬头挺胸\N{\rEng}Chin up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.32,0:24:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我是你们的教官辛姆中士\N{\rEng}I am your senior drill instructor, Career Sergeant Zim!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.19,0:24:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,小腹缩紧 双腿并拢\N{\rEng}Suck in that gut! Feet together!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.87,0:24:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我真是衰毙了\N{\rEng}To think this had to happen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.28,0:24:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,一群蠢蛋 算了\N{\rEng}What a bunch of apes. No, strike that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.79,0:24:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你们逊毙了\N{\rEng}You don't rate that good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.16,0:24:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我没见过…\N{\rEng}Never in my life have I seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.96,0:24:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得很好笑？\N{\rEng}Do you think I'm funny? Do I make you laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.25,0:24:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你觉得我是小丑吗？ - 对不起\N{\rEng}- Do you think I'm a comedian, son? - I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.01,0:24:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你们随时都要尊称我为长官\N{\rEng}The first words and the last words out of your stinking holes will be "Sir"!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.22,0:24:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 明白吗？ - 明白 长官\N{\rEng}- Do you get me? - Sir, yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.43,0:24:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,绕着军营跑一圈\N{\rEng}You see that armoury? Run around it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.97,0:24:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫你跑就跑\N{\rEng}Run, I said! Run, run, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.39,0:24:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 布隆斯基 跟他跑！ - 快！ 快！\N{\rEng}- Bronski, keep pace! - Move! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.48,0:24:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你们觉得我太狠太不公平\N{\rEng}Now, anytime you think I'm being too tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.06,0:24:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,或是开始想念老妈\N{\rEng}anytime you think I'm being unfair...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.02,0:24:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那就马上退出\N{\rEng}anytime you miss your mommy, quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.61,0:24:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,填好表格 签名 打包\N{\rEng}You sign form 1240-A, you grab your gear...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.11,0:24:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,走上失败者的路\N{\rEng}you take a stroll down Washout Lane!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.74,0:24:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,明不明白？\N{\rEng}Do you get me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.58,0:24:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 明白 长官！ - 可悲\N{\rEng}- Sir, yes, sir! - Pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.91,0:24:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,全是一群孬种 不知道这里有没有好汉\N{\rEng}I wonder if there's a handful of guts in the whole bunch of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.25,0:25:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,谁认为他有办法打倒我？\N{\rEng}Now, who here thinks they got what it takes to knock me down?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.38,0:25:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我能 长官\N{\rEng}Sir! I guess maybe I do, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.93,0:25:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,哦！ 天哪！ 天哪！\N{\rEng}Ow! God! God!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.40,0:25:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你没事吧？ - 没事 长官\N{\rEng}- You all right, son? - Sir, yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.69,0:25:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我的手好像断了\N{\rEng}It's my arm. I think it's broken, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.07,0:25:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 医官！ - 天哪\N{\rEng}- Medic! - God.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.03,0:25:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,痛是心里想的\N{\rEng}Pain is in your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.04,0:25:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 下一个是谁？ - 长官\N{\rEng}- Who's next? - Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.04,0:25:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,新兵弗洛斯报到 长官\N{\rEng}Recruit Flores reporting for duty, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.30,0:25:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你特别要求转到这单位？\N{\rEng}You specifically requested transfer from Fort Cronkite to this training unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.97,0:25:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说这里是最严格的\N{\rEng}Sir, I heard it was the best, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.76,0:25:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,的确是最严格\N{\rEng}It is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.97,0:25:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你凭什么以为自己够资格？\N{\rEng}But what makes you think you're good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.82,0:26:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这女孩有种当班长\N{\rEng}Now that's the kind of gal who makes squad leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.95,0:26:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我才要当班长\N{\rEng}That's my job you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.35,0:26:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我很想宰了辛姆中士\N{\rEng}You know, I'd like to kill that Sergeant Zim.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.23,0:26:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你的态度很不好 - 小心\N{\rEng}- Whoa, improper attitude! - Watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.81,0:26:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这样会被踢出去 - 再见吧\N{\rEng}- They'll kick you out for talking like that. - Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.02,0:26:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定会走上失败走路\N{\rEng}There you go down Washout Lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.19,0:26:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没种就是没种\N{\rEng}Yup, you either got what it takes, or you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.69,0:26:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们在排队 - 你也要等 王牌\N{\rEng}- Hey, there is a line. - Wait your turn, Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.99,0:26:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,别紧张 小兵 反正菜都很烂\N{\rEng}Hey, at ease, little soldier. It's all the same muck.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.74,0:26:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,乖乖去排队\N{\rEng}Get in line like everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.46,0:27:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你这阔少爷真有种\N{\rEng}You got some guts for a rich kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.42,0:27:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们交个朋友 如何？\N{\rEng}I guess you and me could be buddies. What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.55,0:27:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真是荣幸 - 当然 我最够朋友了\N{\rEng}- I'm honoured. - Hey! Of course you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.81,0:27:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人都应该有个像我这样的朋友\N{\rEng}Everybody should have a friend like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.02,0:27:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,王牌 到后面排队吧\N{\rEng}Come on, Ace. Back of the line now! Back of the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.73,0:27:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真是个混蛋 - 讨厌鬼\N{\rEng}- What a jerk, man. - Tough guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.44,0:27:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞哥 跟我一起吃饭\N{\rEng}Hey, Rico, want to sit together?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.48,0:27:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不 谢了\N{\rEng}No thanks, Diz.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.20,0:27:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什么问题？\N{\rEng}What's your malfunction, Rico?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.53,0:27:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是问题\N{\rEng}You are.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.58,0:27:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我想一个人入伍 你却硬要跟来\N{\rEng}I joined up to get out on my own, and you had to tag along.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.54,0:27:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为我为你入伍？\N{\rEng}You think I joined the Mobile Infantry because of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.92,0:27:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你敢说不是？\N{\rEng}You saying you didn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.26,0:27:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\rEng}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.59,0:27:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,想都别想 王牌 你不行的\N{\rEng}Forget about it, Ace. You don't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.26,0:28:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你就能当班长？\N{\rEng}What makes you even think you're gonna make squad leader, Rico?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.22,0:28:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我比你有料 - 哈！\N{\rEng}- Something I got, you don't. - Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.98,0:28:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有钱少爷只会装阔 - 才不\N{\rEng}- You rich kids are all the same. - It isn't about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.85,0:28:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这得靠能力 - 嘿！\N{\rEng}- It's about who's the best. - Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.33,0:28:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,第三班\N{\rEng}Third squad!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.63,0:28:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,长官 我不懂\N{\rEng}Sir, I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.67,0:28:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,在核战争中何必用刀？\N{\rEng}Who needs a knife in a nuke fight, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.01,0:28:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,只要按下按钮就行 长官\N{\rEng}All you gotta do is push a button, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.76,0:28:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,暂停 手放在墙上 伞兵\N{\rEng}Cease fire. Put your hand on that wall, trooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.60,0:28:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,把手放在墙上\N{\rEng}Put your hand on that wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.53,0:28:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\rEng}Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.87,0:29:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人的手掌受伤就不能按钮\N{\rEng}The enemy cannot push a button if you disable his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.88,0:29:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,医官\N{\rEng}Medic!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.92,0:29:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有一个共同点\N{\rEng}Ah, well, we all have one thing in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.51,0:29:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都蠢到要参加机动部队\N{\rEng}We were all stupid enough to sign up for Mobile Infantry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.51,0:29:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 布雷肯瑞奇 你为何加入？ - 我全家都是农夫\N{\rEng}- Breckinridge, what's your excuse? - Oh, my family's all farmers.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.68,0:29:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我讨厌务农 而机动部队…\N{\rEng}I hate farming. I mean, uh, Mobile Infantry...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.68,0:29:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,比起来就像是在野餐\N{\rEng}It's like pure picnic by comparison.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.69,0:29:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,乡巴佬真是又蠢又壮对不对？\N{\rEng}All right, so they grow 'em big and dumb on the farm planet, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.19,0:29:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 而且帅！ - 我就爱壮汉\N{\rEng}- And pretty! - I like big!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.65,0:29:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 蒂嘉娜 你呢？ - 我想要从政\N{\rEng}- Djana'D, what about you? - Oh, I'm going in for politics...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.69,0:29:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,想从政就得成为公民\N{\rEng}and, you know, you gotta be a citizen for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.86,0:29:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 所以我就来了 - 你想负起责任\N{\rEng}- So here I am. - Ah, you want some responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.03,0:29:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对 - 苏杰米 接着说吧\N{\rEng}- Yeah. - Shujimi, come on, let's keep it goin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.37,0:29:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我被哈佛大学取录\N{\rEng}I got into Harvard, but my father says forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.87,0:29:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我老爸嫌学费太贵\N{\rEng}It's gonna cost an arm and a leg, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.21,0:29:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,只要服役\N{\rEng}So, if I serve,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.00,0:29:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,就能赚取学费\N{\rEng}Federation pays my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.71,0:29:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我想生孩子\N{\rEng}I want to have babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.21,0:29:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,公民比较容易申请执照\N{\rEng}You know, it's a lot easier to get a licence if you've served.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.59,0:29:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 然后呢… - 我要当职业军官\N{\rEng}- So... - I'm going career.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.38,0:30:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,按步就班升上去\N{\rEng}Officer's training. All the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.18,0:30:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,未来的星际元帅 瑞哥 该你了\N{\rEng}Future Sky Marshal. All right, Rico, your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.06,0:30:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不要多管闲事\N{\rEng}Who asked you to be so nosy?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.56,0:30:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么？ 我是坏人吗？ 我想当作家\N{\rEng}What? I'm the-the bad guy? I'm gonna be a writer, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.73,0:30:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,当然能管闲事\N{\rEng}A writer's got a right to be nosy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.56,0:30:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,弗洛雷斯 你和瑞哥都来自布宜诺斯艾利斯\N{\rEng}Hey, Flores, you know Rico from Buenos Aires.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.44,0:30:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他为什么入伍？ - 哦\N{\rEng}- What's his story? - Oh, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.74,0:30:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他是为了一个女孩子\N{\rEng}he's here because of a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.57,0:30:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞哥 大情圣\N{\rEng}Oh, Rico! Lover boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.58,0:30:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他让我感到兴奋 - 他一定会打你\N{\rEng}- He's getting me excited. - He's gonna blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.04,0:30:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,为了你吗？\N{\rEng}Is it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.26,0:30:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们的宿舍 很简陋 不过是我的家\N{\rEng}This is where we live. It's not much, but it's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.10,0:30:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的床铺 我每晚都梦到你\N{\rEng}Right there, that's my bunk, where I dream about you every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.27,0:30:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,训练很辛苦\N{\rEng}Boot's pretty tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.94,0:30:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,有时我很灰心\N{\rEng}Sometimes I think I won't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.65,0:30:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我一想到你就会更努力\N{\rEng}But then I think about what you're doing, and I try harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.86,0:31:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 你介意吗？ - 努力点 宝贝\N{\rEng}- Hey, guys! Do you mind? - Try harder, baby, try harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.66,0:31:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道？ 也许我会成为班长\N{\rEng}Who knows? They might even make me squad leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.79,0:31:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我得上床了\N{\rEng}Uh-oh, I better pack it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.62,0:31:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你 宝贝 我爱你！\N{\rEng}Oh, I love you, baby, I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.30,0:31:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 写信给我 - 我是如此爱你\N{\rEng}- Write me! - I love you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.05,0:31:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我要杀了你 - 我是如此爱你\N{\rEng}- I'm gonna kill you guys! - I love you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.60,0:31:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 再见 记得写信 - 再见！\N{\rEng}- Bye! Write me. - Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.72,0:31:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,五分钟后绕行月球 艾邦妮兹\N{\rEng}Orbit in five, Ibanez.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.89,0:31:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,先到先飞\N{\rEng}First one there gets to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.41,0:31:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 关闭舱门 - 等一下\N{\rEng}- Locking it down. - Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.62,0:31:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,别让艾邦妮兹驾驶 她太疯狂了\N{\rEng}Oh, no. Not Ibanez again. She's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.50,0:31:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,准备 发射\N{\rEng}Ready, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.13,0:32:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好！\N{\rEng}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.30,0:32:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,伸出机翼\N{\rEng}Deploying wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.89,0:32:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛这么开心？\N{\rEng}How come you're in such a good mood, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.39,0:32:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我要开战舰\N{\rEng}'Cause today I get to fly that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.67,0:33:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,飞行受训人员艾邦妮兹报到\N{\rEng}Pilot Trainee Ibanez reporting for duty, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.17,0:33:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,坐在副驾驶座\N{\rEng}Take the number two chair, Ibanez.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.09,0:33:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的 女士 - 看见啦？\N{\rEng}- Yes, ma'am. - You see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.68,0:33:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 辨识身份 - 艾邦妮兹 T325A 正确\N{\rEng}- Identify. - Ibanez, T-3 25-A, clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.94,0:33:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这儿干嘛？\N{\rEng}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.11,0:33:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我要教你驾驶这艘战舰\N{\rEng}I'm the guy whose gonna teach you to fly this crate.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.07,0:33:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,助理教官\N{\rEng}Oh, Assistant Instructor.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.95,0:33:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我该尊称你长官吗？\N{\rEng}Should I call you "sir"?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.54,0:33:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我下命令才要 - 准备起飞\N{\rEng}- Only when I give you an order. - Prepare for departure.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.00,0:34:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到我们会再见面\N{\rEng}It's amazing, us running into each other like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.67,0:34:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 也许是命中注定 - 也许不是\N{\rEng}- Maybe it's fate. - Maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.50,0:34:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说有个女孩很优秀\N{\rEng}Heard about this crazy girl coming through the Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.76,0:34:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,她是天生好手 只是有点野\N{\rEng}Solid math, a little wild on the stick, but a natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.47,0:34:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道是你\N{\rEng}And when it turned out to be you,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.01,0:34:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,就安排和你见面\N{\rEng}I just made sure that we would run into each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.31,0:34:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,杨罗杰号可以起飞\N{\rEng}Rodger Young cleared for undocking and departure.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.10,0:34:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 艾邦妮兹\N{\rEng}All right, Ibanez.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.02,0:34:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 开出去吧 - 是的 女士\N{\rEng}- Take her out. - Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.65,0:34:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,系统正常\N{\rEng}All systems go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.51,0:34:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,进行模拟飞行时老师都跟不上我\N{\rEng}In simulation, my supervisors could never keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.18,0:34:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是模拟飞行\N{\rEng}Well, this isn't simulation any more...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.06,0:34:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,小心点 军校生\N{\rEng}so take her out easy, cadet.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.77,0:35:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 长官\N{\rEng}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.11,0:35:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,距离五米\N{\rEng}Five metres from object.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.82,0:35:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,距离三米\N{\rEng}Three metres from object.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.12,0:35:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,通过\N{\rEng}Clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.46,0:35:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别超过起飞速限 - 否则呢？\N{\rEng}- Don't exceed port speed. - Or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.50,0:35:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你的飞行权会被取消 还有我的\N{\rEng}Or they revoke your flight status, and mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.97,0:35:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你的前途掌握在我手上\N{\rEng}Your career is in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.52,0:35:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢来 副驾驶\N{\rEng}Steady as she goes, Number Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.98,0:35:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 准备超光速飞行 - 是的\N{\rEng}- Prepare for warp. - Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.32,0:35:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,一号 计算木星航道\N{\rEng}Number One, design for Jupiter orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.65,0:35:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,准备转换超光速引擎\N{\rEng}All crew, all sections, stand by to cut in C-drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.57,0:35:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,五…四…\N{\rEng}Star drive in five, four...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.41,0:36:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,准备 稳定…\N{\rEng}ready, steady...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.79,0:36:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,启动\N{\rEng}go!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.36,0:36:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,快进攻 快！\N{\rEng}We're going in! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.24,0:36:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们冲不破防线\N{\rEng}Man, they're defended. No way in.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.12,0:36:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 翻跳动作 - 什么？\N{\rEng}- Flip six, three hole. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.58,0:36:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你做翻跳动作就能得分\N{\rEng}You run a flip six, three hole play, and you can score.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.42,0:36:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 掩护我 - 好\N{\rEng}- Cover me. - You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.26,0:36:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,上吧\N{\rEng}Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.48,0:37:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢了 哥们 - 杂种\N{\rEng}- Thanks, buddy. - Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.11,0:37:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯！\N{\rEng}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.12,0:37:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那小子很灵活\N{\rEng}Kid's got some moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.25,0:37:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,让他当班长 看看他的能耐\N{\rEng}Give him a squad. See what he can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.13,0:37:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,小猫咪\N{\rEng}Kitty, Kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.01,0:37:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我得教你们打台球\N{\rEng}Someone's got to teach you guys how to play some pool here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.76,0:37:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧他\N{\rEng}Look at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.26,0:37:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那副得意样 真自傲\N{\rEng}Have you ever seen anybody so pleased with himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.10,0:37:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,辛姆一定得选个乖乖牌\N{\rEng}Well, Zim must have had to choose someone to be his brownnose.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.90,0:37:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,没有你我就办不到\N{\rEng}I couldn't have done it without you, Diz.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.74,0:38:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友\N{\rEng}Friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.42,0:38:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 泰勒 - 我在这儿\N{\rEng}- Niler. - Yeah, here I am. Ah, great, my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.63,0:38:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,没了 大伙\N{\rEng}That's all, folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.10,0:38:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 强尼\N{\rEng}Hi, Johnny.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.64,0:38:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉没早点写信给你\N{\rEng}I'm sorry I haven't written you sooner, but, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.31,0:38:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,噢…瑞哥 你配不上她\N{\rEng}Oh, Rico,it's been really busy.you don't deserve that!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.98,0:38:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘘 嘘 - 他们真的在这里\N{\rEng}- Shh, shh. - They've really got us going here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.02,0:38:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定当上班长\N{\rEng}They must have made you squad leader by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.65,0:38:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,没有的话 叫他们来找我\N{\rEng}And if they haven't, tell 'em to talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.15,0:38:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你瞧 找到好女人就不用愁\N{\rEng}See? All it takes is the love of a good woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.99,0:38:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 看这儿 - 别看了\N{\rEng}- Look at that.Look at those. - Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.83,0:38:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不是很美吗？\N{\rEng}Isn't it beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.83,0:38:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我好爱这儿\N{\rEng}I love it out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.17,0:38:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是问题\N{\rEng}That's also the problem
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.88,0:38:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,因为 我想当职业军人\N{\rEng}Because I think I'm gonna go career.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.43,0:39:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我要指挥战舰\N{\rEng}I want to command a ship of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.89,0:39:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一来…\N{\rEng}And you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.52,0:39:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就没时间\N{\rEng}I don't think that's gonna leave a lot of room...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.02,0:39:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,交往 强尼\N{\rEng}for you and me, Johnny.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.56,0:39:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你会很失望\N{\rEng}I know that's not what you wanted to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.19,0:39:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,可是\N{\rEng}But, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.70,0:39:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我得把握机会 对不起\N{\rEng}I have to follow my heart. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.08,0:39:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,写信给我\N{\rEng}Write me, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.21,0:39:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们永远当好朋友\N{\rEng}Write me so that I know we'll always be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.97,0:39:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 让我们回到游戏 - 我觉得很对不起强尼\N{\rEng}- Let's get back to the game. - I feel so sorry for Johnny.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.23,0:39:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,她们总是伤透你的心\N{\rEng}Funny how they always want to be friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.64,0:39:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,之后还想做好朋友\N{\rEng}after they rip your guts out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.56,0:39:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我是活该\N{\rEng}Yeah. Well, it's what I deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.86,0:40:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思？\N{\rEng}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.61,0:40:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我会入伍全是为了她\N{\rEng}Oh, I joined up for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.76,0:41:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,该死 布雷肯瑞奇 别挡住我\N{\rEng}Hey! Goddam it, Breckinridge, clear my line of fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.22,0:41:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我的头盔坏了\N{\rEng}It's my helmet! It's all screwed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.27,0:41:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你会碍事的\N{\rEng}You're gonna blow the score!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.10,0:41:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 蠢蛋 - 妈的！\N{\rEng}- Damn! - Dumb shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.73,0:41:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,快前进 怎么了？\N{\rEng}Diz, stay put! What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.23,0:41:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 头盔有问题 - 给我\N{\rEng}- Damn thing keeps getting in my way! - Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.11,0:41:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,每次出错都是你的问题\N{\rEng}How come whenever something goes wrong, it's always you, Breckinridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.48,0:41:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为我又蠢又壮\N{\rEng}It must be 'cause I'm big and dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.99,0:41:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\rEng}Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.66,0:41:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,医官\N{\rEng}Medic!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.33,0:41:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞哥 你被解除班长职位\N{\rEng}Rico, you are relieved of squad command!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.00,0:41:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是你准许新兵脱下头盔吗？\N{\rEng}Rico, did you give the recruit permission to remove his helmet?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.09,0:41:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 长官 布雷肯瑞奇说他的头盔坏了\N{\rEng}Sir, yes, sir. Breckinridge reported a helmet malfunction...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.05,0:41:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我要他拿给我看\N{\rEng}and I asked him to show it to me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.76,0:41:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你会修理M-3型头盔吗？\N{\rEng}Are you rated to repair the M-3 Tactical Helmet, Rico?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.23,0:41:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不会 长官\N{\rEng}Sir, no, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.77,0:41:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那么你为何在实弹演习时…\N{\rEng}Then why did you order your man to remove his helmet...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.77,0:42:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,叫他脱下头盔？\N{\rEng}during a live fire exercise?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.44,0:42:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要每名队员尽全力\N{\rEng}Sir, I needed everyone in my squad operational, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.11,0:42:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要获胜 长官\N{\rEng}I wanted to win, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.49,0:42:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,继续\N{\rEng}Carry on.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.30,0:42:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,军士 我们因为此事失去两名新兵\N{\rEng}Sergeant, we've already lost two recruits over this incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.01,0:42:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为这个人还有前途吗？\N{\rEng}Do you think there's any possibility of salvaging this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.93,0:42:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,有的 长官\N{\rEng}Yes, sir, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.60,0:42:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEng}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.48,0:42:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,让他接受行政处罚\N{\rEng}We'll try administrative punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.15,0:42:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,囚犯 站住\N{\rEng}Prisoner, halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.88,0:43:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,用力咬\N{\rEng}Bite down on this, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.88,0:43:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,很有用 我很清楚\N{\rEng}It helps. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.77,0:43:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他指挥无能\N{\rEng}For incompetence of command...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.90,0:43:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,在实弹演习中…\N{\rEng}for failure to abide by safety regulations...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.61,0:43:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,违反安全规定…\N{\rEng}during a live fire exercise...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.11,0:43:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他的疏失导致一名士兵死亡\N{\rEng}for negligence which contributed to the death of a teammate...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.87,0:43:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,新兵强尼·瑞哥\N{\rEng}recruit trainee John Rico...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.20,0:43:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,必须受刑…\N{\rEng}is sentenced to administrative punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.96,0:43:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,十下鞭刑\N{\rEng}Ten lashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.13,0:43:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,开始行刑\N{\rEng}You may carry out the sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.34,0:43:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,一…\N{\rEng}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.93,0:43:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,二…\N{\rEng}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.77,0:44:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,三…\N{\rEng}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.15,0:44:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,四…\N{\rEng}Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.07,0:44:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,五…\N{\rEng}Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.24,0:44:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,六…\N{\rEng}Six!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.24,0:44:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,七…\N{\rEng}Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.24,0:44:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,八…\N{\rEng}Eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.91,0:44:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,九…\N{\rEng}Nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.92,0:44:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,十！\N{\rEng}Ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.61,0:44:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了 你猜中我的心意\N{\rEng}Thanks. You read my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.32,0:44:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,下半夜更最难熬\N{\rEng}Oh, third watch always seems to last forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.53,0:44:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不一定\N{\rEng}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.28,0:44:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这得看你和谁一起值班\N{\rEng}It depends on who you're spending it with.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.54,0:45:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,出了问题\N{\rEng}Something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.83,0:45:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那儿 - 我重新设定航道\N{\rEng}- There. - No, I replotted the course.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.92,0:45:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这样更有效率 - 你才来了三个星期…\N{\rEng}- It's more efficient this way. - Three weeks aboard a starship...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.17,0:45:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,就想跟我比？\N{\rEng}and you think that you can lick my navs?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.51,0:45:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管查\N{\rEng}Check it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.93,0:45:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我和达拉第舰长谈过\N{\rEng}You know, I was talking with Captain Deladier...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.10,0:45:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,她说…\N{\rEng}and, uh, she said...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.65,0:45:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,别转移话题\N{\rEng}Don't change the subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.32,0:45:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我对不对？\N{\rEng}Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.99,0:45:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,“新航道最佳” 你做得对\N{\rEng}Yeah. Yeah. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.08,0:45:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那么舰长怎么说？\N{\rEng}So, what did the captain say?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.83,0:45:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,她说我们应该正式搭档…\N{\rEng}She thinks that we ought to team up officially...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.63,0:45:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,为她服务\N{\rEng}and crew for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.51,0:45:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你和我？ - 我们是好搭档 卡门\N{\rEng}- You and me, huh? - We're good together, Carmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.09,0:46:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,各方面都领先\N{\rEng}We're way ahead of the curve in every department.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.51,0:46:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们很有默契\N{\rEng}I can anticipate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.60,0:46:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我要什么\N{\rEng}You know what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.02,0:46:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 你要什么？\N{\rEng}No. What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.11,0:46:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,太空中有重力场\N{\rEng}There's a gravity field out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.24,0:46:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 进行扫瞄 启动 - 那儿\N{\rEng}- Run a scan. Sensors on. - There.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.21,0:46:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 重力2.25 继续增加… - 报告\N{\rEng}- Gravity at 225 and rising. - Report.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.54,0:46:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,船长 前方有不明物体\N{\rEng}Captain, we're in the path of an unidentified object...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.59,0:46:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,向我们快速冲来…\N{\rEng}moving toward us at high speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.38,0:46:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,根据资料应该是小行星\N{\rEng}Profile suggests an asteroid, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.70,0:46:49.94,Chs,,0,0,0,,“撞击警告”
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.94,0:46:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 六秒后撞击 - 紧急闪躲动作\N{\rEng}- Impact, six seconds! - Emergency evasion!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.65,0:47:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,三…二…\N{\rEng}Three, two,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.24,0:47:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,启动\N{\rEng}fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.42,0:47:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,关闭21号舱门\N{\rEng}Close compartment 21!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.32,0:47:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,从哪儿来的？\N{\rEng}Where'd it come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.82,0:47:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,从虫族隔离区来的\N{\rEng}It came out of the Arachnid Quarantine Zone, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.61,0:47:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,通讯官通知舰队小行星接近中\N{\rEng}Number Four, contact Fleet. Tell 'em there's a loose asteroid headed their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.62,0:47:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,通讯失效 全都被摧毁\N{\rEng}Communications are down, ma'am. They're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.45,0:47:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 估计损失 - 舰身受损\N{\rEng}- Damage assessment. - Hull's compromised.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.46,0:47:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没死掉真走运\N{\rEng}We're lucky to be alive, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.04,0:47:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是靠运气\N{\rEng}Luck didn't have anything to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.25,0:47:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的飞行小组很优秀\N{\rEng}We have a hell of a flight team.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.48,0:48:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能离开\N{\rEng}It really stinks, you going.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.94,0:48:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,机动部队没有我也一样\N{\rEng}Yeah, well, the Mobile Infantry will just have to get along without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.99,0:48:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我不懂 瑞哥 你接受了惩罚\N{\rEng}I don't get it, Rico. You took your licks.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.91,0:48:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们不想要你 可以把你踢走\N{\rEng}If they didn't want you, they would have kicked you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.66,0:48:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿…\N{\rEng}Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.54,0:48:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我不该入伍 我害死人…\N{\rEng}I joined up for the wrong reasons. I got a guy killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.66,0:48:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这就证明我没有能力\N{\rEng}I figure that kind of proves I don't have what it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.08,0:48:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞哥 电话接通了\N{\rEng}Rico, your call's going through.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.71,0:48:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,去接\N{\rEng}Take it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.68,0:48:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 喂？ 强尼 - 嗨 妈妈\N{\rEng}- Hello? Oh, Johnny! - Hi, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.06,0:48:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,比尔 快接电话 是强尼\N{\rEng}B-Bill, pick it up. It's Johnny!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.19,0:48:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 强尼？ - 爸爸\N{\rEng}- Johnny? - Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.06,0:48:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你的制服呢？ - 比尔…\N{\rEng}- Where's your uniform? - Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.27,0:49:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,见到你真好\N{\rEng}It's just good to hear from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.28,0:49:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你好吗？ 儿子？\N{\rEng}How are you, son?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.65,0:49:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我不适合这里 爸爸\N{\rEng}It's not really working out here for me, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.99,0:49:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想…\N{\rEng}I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.57,0:49:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道我能不能回家\N{\rEng}I was hoping it would be all right if I came home.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.58,0:49:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,当然能 马上回来\N{\rEng}Well, of-of course. You should come home immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.04,0:49:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 我太傻了\N{\rEng}I'm sorry. I've been an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.37,0:49:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,别这么说 你先回家…\N{\rEng}Don't talk like that. You just come on home...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.75,0:49:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们再好好谈谈\N{\rEng}talk things out.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.55,0:49:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们很爱你 儿子\N{\rEng}We love you, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.38,0:49:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那是什么？ - 好像要下雨\N{\rEng}- My, what's that? - Looks like rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.05,0:49:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这时候？ - 外面好暗\N{\rEng}- This time of year? - Sure is dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.80,0:49:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,大气干扰导致…\N{\rEng}Your transmission has been terminated...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.60,0:49:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,通讯中断\N{\rEng}due to atmospheric interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.23,0:49:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,请稍后再试\N{\rEng}Please try your call again later.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.40,0:49:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,再见了\N{\rEng}Well, see ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.07,0:49:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你就这样退出…\N{\rEng}Hey, you take that stroll down Washout Lane...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.57,0:49:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,只证明一件事\N{\rEng}you're only proving one thing,Johnny.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.49,0:49:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事？\N{\rEng}What's that, Diz?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.41,0:49:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有资格当公民\N{\rEng}That you don't have what it takes to be a citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.11,0:50:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事？\N{\rEng}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.28,0:50:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 发生什么事？\N{\rEng}Hey, hey, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.79,0:50:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事？\N{\rEng}Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.62,0:50:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨 Kitten 怎么回事？ - 战争 我们要去参战了…\N{\rEng}- Hey, Kitten, what's going on? - It's war! We're going to war!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.63,0:50:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这次的灾难前所未有\N{\rEng}The devastation we are seeing is unparalleled.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.34,0:50:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,根据估计有数百万人丧命 一座城市全毁\N{\rEng}Judging from early estimates, millions dead, a city in ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.30,0:50:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那是日内瓦吗？\N{\rEng}Is that Geneva?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.47,0:50:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,强尼 是该死的大虫攻击我们\N{\rEng}Goddam bugs whacked us, Johnny.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.39,0:50:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,虫族从大本营克兰达夫星球…\N{\rEng}The meteor was shot out of orbit by bug plasma...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.81,0:51:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,发射电浆把陨石撞离轨道\N{\rEng}that derived from Klendathu, the Arachnids'home planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.99,0:51:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这个曾被称为拉丁乐园的城市片瓦不留\N{\rEng}Nothing lives in what was once called the Latin Paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.58,0:51:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,强尼 那是我们…\N{\rEng}Oh,Johnny, it's us.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.00,0:51:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,布宜诺斯艾利斯完全消失\N{\rEng}Buenos Aires has been wiped off the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.25,0:51:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,…我们的家\N{\rEng}That's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.34,0:51:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才联邦委员会一致表决…\N{\rEng}The Federal Council met moments ago and voted unanimously...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.43,0:51:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,全体动员消灭虫族大敌\N{\rEng}for mobilization to destroy the Arachnid threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.06,0:51:40.17,Chs,,0,0,0,,“8 764 608人死亡”
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.06,0:51:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我是认真的 我要去 - 辛姆 你得留下来\N{\rEng}- I'm serious. I'll go anywhere. - Forget it, Zim. We need you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.27,0:51:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我要打仗 - 只有一种方法能让你去打仗…\N{\rEng}- I want combat, sir. - The only way you're gonna see combat...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.28,0:51:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,被降为二等兵！\N{\rEng}is if you bust yourself to private!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.28,0:51:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 明白？ - 我明白 长官\N{\rEng}- Get me? - Yes, sir, I get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.37,0:51:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 长官 - 你要做什么？ 瑞哥\N{\rEng}- Sir! - What do you want, Rico?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.58,0:51:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我要收回退出的要求\N{\rEng}I wish to reconsider my request to drop out, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.71,0:52:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经签好表格\N{\rEng}You already signed your 1240-A, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.87,0:52:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那是非法的 - 少校 我不该退出\N{\rEng}- It wouldn't be legal. - Major, I know it was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.63,0:52:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我没吸取教训 反而又犯错\N{\rEng}I didn't learn from one mistake, and I made another, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.46,0:52:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你做出决定\N{\rEng}You made your decision, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.47,0:52:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,长官 我全家都在布宜诺斯艾利斯\N{\rEng}Sir, my family, my whole family, was in Buenos Aires, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.06,0:52:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞哥 这是你的签名吗？\N{\rEng}Is this your signature, Rico?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.23,0:52:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 长官\N{\rEng}Sir, yes, it is, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.61,0:52:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来不像\N{\rEng}Doesn't look like it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.07,0:52:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 去吧 二等兵 - 是的 长官\N{\rEng}- Carry on, Private! - Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.79,0:52:41.85,Chs,,0,0,0,,“联邦电视网”
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.17,0:52:44.45,Chs,,0,0,0,,“战争”
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.05,0:52:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,看到布宜诺斯艾利斯市的残骸先是悲痛\N{\rEng}Out of the ashes of Buenos Aires comes first sorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.18,0:52:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来是愤怒\N{\rEng}then anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.89,0:52:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,只有死虫才是好虫子\N{\rEng}The only good bug is a dead bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.93,0:53:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,联邦委员会在日内瓦开会\N{\rEng}In Geneva, the Federal Council convenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.10,0:53:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须誓死…\N{\rEng}We must meet the threat with our valour, our blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.90,0:53:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,勇敢面对挑战\N{\rEng}indeed, with our very lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.19,0:53:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,捍卫人类文明\N{\rEng}to ensure that human civilization, not insect...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.86,0:53:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,别让虫族永远统治银河系\N{\rEng}dominates this galaxy, now and always!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.03,0:53:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,狄恩元帅…\N{\rEng}Sky Marshal Dienes announces plans...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.70,0:53:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,向虫族陨石来源…\N{\rEng}for an offensive against Klendathu...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.74,0:53:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,克兰达夫星球宣战\N{\rEng}source of the bug meteor that destroyed Buenos Aires.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.66,0:53:27.75,Chs,,0,0,0,,“你想知道更多吗？”
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.75,0:53:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,联邦科学家每天不断研究新方法消灭虫族\N{\rEng}Every day, Federal scientists are looking for new ways to kill bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.25,0:53:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,一般的虫族战士很笨…\N{\rEng}Your basic Arachnid warrior isn't too smart...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.72,0:53:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,可是打断它的一只脚…\N{\rEng}but you can blow off a limb...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.89,0:53:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,它却能保留八成战斗力\N{\rEng}and it's still 86 percent combat effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.56,0:53:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个窍门：瞄准神经干 把它撂倒\N{\rEng}Here's a tip.:Aim for the nerve stem, and put it down for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.73,0:53:51.82,Chs,,0,0,0,,你想知道更多吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.07,0:53:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,人人都出力 你呢\N{\rEng}Everyone's doing their part. Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.28,0:53:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,战争需要每个人贡献力量\N{\rEng}Die! Die! The war effort needs your effort...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.91,0:54:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,家庭 工作和社区…\N{\rEng}at work, at home, in your community.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.08,0:54:06.12,Chs,,0,0,0,,“胜利倒数”
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.12,0:54:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是…\N{\rEng}We now break net and take you live...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.92,0:54:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,位于虫族隔离区的…\N{\rEng}to Fleet Battle Station Ticonderoga...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.29,0:54:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,提康德鲁加星际战舰基地\N{\rEng}deep inside the Arachnid Quarantine Zone...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.92,0:54:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,英勇的星舰战将准备出击\N{\rEng}where the men and women of the Federal Armed Services prepare to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.59,0:54:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,准备连线…开始\N{\rEng}D XQ uplink on two, one. You're on.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.60,0:54:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这里没人知道何时开始…\N{\rEng}No one here in the AQZ knows exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.93,0:54:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,进攻克兰达夫星\N{\rEng}when the invasion of Klendathu will occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.27,0:54:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都在猜\N{\rEng}But everyone's talking about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.10,0:54:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得也许是明天\N{\rEng}and the talk says tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.10,0:54:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,看来机动部队想大嚼虫族\N{\rEng}Here's a bunch of MI kids that look like they could eat bugs for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.11,0:54:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好吃 好吃 好吃 - 大兵\N{\rEng}- Yum, yum, yum. - So, trooper,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.11,0:54:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你不怕大虫吗？\N{\rEng}you're not too worried about fighting the Arachnids?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.94,0:54:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,只要发射一枚核弹 大虫就死翘翘\N{\rEng}Hey, shoot a nuke down a bug hole, you got a lot of dead bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.70,0:54:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,希望全炸死之前 我能打死几只虫\N{\rEng}Am I right? I just hope it's not over before we get some.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.87,0:54:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 得了 - 有人说虫族生态…\N{\rEng}- Okay, come on. - Some say the bugs were provoked...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.79,0:54:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,遭到了破坏才对人类反击\N{\rEng}by the intrusion of humans into their natural habitat...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.54,0:54:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们该和平共处不该对虫族开战\N{\rEng}that a "live and let live policy" is preferable to war with the bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.63,0:54:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉你\N{\rEng}Let me tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.13,0:54:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我是布宜诺斯艾利斯市人 我要消灭它们\N{\rEng}I'm from Buenos Aires, and I say kill them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.30,0:54:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对 - 继续\N{\rEng}- Yeah! - Go on,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.71,0:54:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对！ - 对啊！\N{\rEng}- Yeah! - Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.22,0:55:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,狠角色\N{\rEng}Big bad bugs, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.22,0:55:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们要去纹身\N{\rEng}Hey, guys, we ought to get tattoos.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.39,0:55:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一起去吧 - 好\N{\rEng}- Hey, let's all get cut together. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.80,0:55:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 纹身干嘛？ - 什么？\N{\rEng}- What do I want a tattoo for? - Oh, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.22,0:55:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你的皮肤太嫩吗？\N{\rEng}Your skin's too pretty? Come on, everybody's doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.89,0:55:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,强尼\N{\rEng}Hey,Johnny!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.56,0:55:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,强尼·瑞哥\N{\rEng}Johnny Rico.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.23,0:55:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,卡门\N{\rEng}Carmen?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.53,0:55:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,稍息\N{\rEng}Oh. At ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.91,0:55:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我休假 最好别戴军帽\N{\rEng}Guess I ought to lose the hat when I'm off duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.03,0:55:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨 蒂丝 - 卡门\N{\rEng}- Hi, Diz. - Carmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.54,0:55:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈说得对\N{\rEng}My mother was right about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.25,0:55:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你穿制服很好看\N{\rEng}You look great in a uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.17,0:55:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你也挺帅的\N{\rEng}You look pretty good yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.97,0:55:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什么消息？\N{\rEng}So, what do you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.97,0:55:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,布宜诺斯艾利斯有没有人生还？\N{\rEng}You know about anyone who made it out of BA alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.01,0:55:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我试着不多想\N{\rEng}Most of the time I don't think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.68,0:55:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,假装是别人的事\N{\rEng}Like it happened to someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.39,0:55:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,可是突然觉醒时就哭个不停\N{\rEng}Then it hits me, and I, uh, can't stop crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.69,0:55:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还活着 这值得高兴\N{\rEng}Well, we're still alive. Got to be happy about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.52,0:55:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到我好像不高兴\N{\rEng}You don't look very happy to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.90,0:56:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我该高兴吗？\N{\rEng}Should I be?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.36,0:56:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,强尼 现在不同 我们在打仗\N{\rEng}Johnny, it's different now. We're at war.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.20,0:56:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们分开对你我都好\N{\rEng}I mean, I think what I did was probably the best thing for both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.37,0:56:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧 中尉？\N{\rEng}Everything copacetic, Lieutenant?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.54,0:56:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,山德 记得强尼吗？\N{\rEng}Zander, you remember Johnny.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.04,0:56:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我和山德是飞行搭档\N{\rEng}Zander and I are a flight team now.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.38,0:56:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,舰队最好的小组\N{\rEng}Yeah, and we're best in the fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.55,0:56:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂了\N{\rEng}I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.30,0:56:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这样对你我最好\N{\rEng}This is the part that's best for both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.22,0:56:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别再装了… - 强尼 等等\N{\rEng}- Don't do me any more favours. - Johnny, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.89,0:56:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,算了 他是机动部队\N{\rEng}No, forget it, Lieutenant. He's Mobile Infantry.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.23,0:56:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他们只会杀人\N{\rEng}See, when you're trained to kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.23,0:56:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不懂得礼貌\N{\rEng}it just doesn't pay to be polite.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.73,0:56:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你对机动部队有意见吗？\N{\rEng}You got something to say about the Mobile Infantry?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.07,0:56:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你听得很清楚\N{\rEng}I think you heard me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.03,0:56:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你想打架吗 二等兵？\N{\rEng}You want to make something of it, Private?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.87,0:56:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我不跟军官打架\N{\rEng}Not with an officer. No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.20,0:56:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 机动部队不是蠢蛋 - 我就撇开官阶\N{\rEng}- The MI doesn't mint stupid troopers. - Well, let's disregard rank.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.04,0:56:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,山德 别这样\N{\rEng}Zander, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.37,0:56:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,听到吗？ 这无关官阶\N{\rEng}Everybody hear that? Rank is not an issue here.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.92,0:57:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别这样 - 他敢怎样？\N{\rEng}- Don't do this. - Come on. What's he gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.85,0:57:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,来呀 臭大兵！\N{\rEng}Come on, jarheads!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.48,0:57:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我要宰了你\N{\rEng}Let go of me! Come on! I'm gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.98,0:57:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你好看\N{\rEng}I'm gonna kill you! I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.03,0:57:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,住手 快\N{\rEng}Guys! Guys! Quit it! Come on! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.70,0:57:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他不值得 - 快 快\N{\rEng}- He's not worth it! - Come on! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.99,0:57:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞哥 算了 机动部队和舰队一向不合\N{\rEng}Forget it, Rico! Mobile Infantry and Fleet don't mix. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.00,0:57:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 走吧\N{\rEng}Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.80,0:57:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,臭大兵\N{\rEng}Jarheads.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.63,0:57:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 机动部队万岁 - 耶！\N{\rEng}- Mobile Infantry rules! - Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.47,0:57:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,痛死了\N{\rEng}Oh, God, that hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.60,0:57:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我有办法让你更痛\N{\rEng}Hey, well, I got something that might hurt just a little bit more, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.31,0:57:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要打仗 一定会赢\N{\rEng}Oh, yeah! We're gonna fight, and we're gonna win!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.73,0:58:01.39,Chs,,0,0,0,,“死神降临”
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.50,0:58:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我是舰长\N{\rEng}This is the captain speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.33,0:58:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,全体人员准备降落\N{\rEng}All personnel prepare for drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.63,0:58:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,倒数三分钟\N{\rEng}We are at D-minus three and counting.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.51,0:58:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是先锋部队\N{\rEng}We are going in with first wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.68,0:58:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人最多\N{\rEng}Means more bugs for us to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.89,0:58:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,彻底消灭敌区\N{\rEng}You smash the entire area.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.48,0:58:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,杀死所有长两只脚以上的东西\N{\rEng}You kill anything that has more than two legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.65,0:58:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 明白吗？ - 我们明白 长官\N{\rEng}- You get me? - We get you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.20,0:59:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 星球表面射出电浆 - 虫族炮火\N{\rEng}- Plasma, ma'am, from the planet. - Bug batteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.12,0:59:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,军事情报说威力应该不强\N{\rEng}According to military intelligence, it'll be random and light.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.62,0:59:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 部队状况？ - 情况是…\N{\rEng}- Drop status? - Drop is...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.29,0:59:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,35%降落到地面\N{\rEng}35 percent complete, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.88,0:59:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢来 副驾驶\N{\rEng}Steady as she goes, Number Two.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.73,1:00:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,记住你的训练 你会活着回去的！\N{\rEng}Remember your training, and you will make it back alive!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.34,1:00:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,电浆威力很强 情报有误\N{\rEng}This isn't random or light. Someone made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.34,1:00:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,部队全都降落了 女士\N{\rEng}That's it. We're empty, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.23,1:00:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,有人犯了大错\N{\rEng}Someone made a big goddam mistake!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.19,1:00:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,快往上飞\N{\rEng}Break for high orbit!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.90,1:01:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,走 走 走！\N{\rEng}Let's go, let's go, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.45,1:01:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,强尼！\N{\rEng}Johnny!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.43,1:02:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,核弹待命\N{\rEng}Rockets up!Rocket crew, move up!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.21,1:02:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 核弹小组 利维 瑞哥… - 把它们炸死\N{\rEng}- Nuke 'em! Levy! Rico! - Heat 'em up!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.88,1:02:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好了 - 发射\N{\rEng}- Set. - Fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.43,1:02:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 跟我来 - 上吧\N{\rEng}- Follow me! - Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.77,1:02:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,第一排 左翼！\N{\rEng}First platoon, left flank!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.90,1:02:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,分散！ 第一 二班 跟我来\N{\rEng}Split up! First and second squads, follow me.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.11,1:03:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,第二班掩护 第一班跟我\N{\rEng}Two, cover! One, with me!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.82,1:03:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,一边到另一边\N{\rEng}Along side! Side to side!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.45,1:03:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,开火\N{\rEng}Fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.01,1:03:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,它们来了\N{\rEng}Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.19,1:03:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 王牌 我们该怎么办？ - 我…不知道\N{\rEng}- Ace, what are we doing? - Uh, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.61,1:03:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不知道 - 把它们全干掉\N{\rEng}- I don't know. - Kill them! Kill them all!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.62,1:03:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,上呀\N{\rEng}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.58,1:03:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,找死吗？\N{\rEng}Come on! Come on! You want some?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.42,1:03:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你们死！\N{\rEng}Here's some! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.59,1:03:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,吃子弹吧\N{\rEng}Here's some of this!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.43,1:04:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天！\N{\rEng}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.60,1:04:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,苏杰米\N{\rEng}Shujimi!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.10,1:04:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 不！\N{\rEng}No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.40,1:04:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,救命！ 救命！ 救命！\N{\rEng}Help! Help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.57,1:04:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不！ 天哪！\N{\rEng}No! God!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.24,1:04:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,快走吧\N{\rEng}Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.00,1:04:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,撤退\N{\rEng}Fall back!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.77,1:04:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？\N{\rEng}All units,What's going on? fall back to retrieval.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.94,1:05:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,收到讯号吗？\N{\rEng}Repeat.You got com? All units...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.44,1:05:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,全体撤退\N{\rEng}fall back to retrieval.It's a general retreat!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.28,1:05:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 回运兵船上！ - 快！\N{\rEng}- Back to the boats! - Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.45,1:05:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,快 我们走！\N{\rEng}Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.78,1:05:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是被称为\N{\rEng}We've just landed here on what cap troopers...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.45,1:05:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,大K星的战场\N{\rEng}are calling Big K...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.62,1:05:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,第六机动部队展开攻击\N{\rEng}with the 6th Mobile Infantry Division.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.21,1:05:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这丑陋的星球全是大虫\N{\rEng}It's an ugly planet, a bug planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.29,1:05:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,威胁人类的生存…\N{\rEng}A planet hostile to life as we...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.89,1:05:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,救命啊！\N{\rEng}Help me!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.56,1:05:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,快向右\N{\rEng}Squad right!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.90,1:05:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,快走 快 快 快…\N{\rEng}Come on! Go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.74,1:05:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,快离开这里\N{\rEng}Get out of here now!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.99,1:05:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 小心点！ - 小心你的侧面！ 小心你的侧面！\N{\rEng}- Watch your step! - Watch your flank! Watch your flank!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.25,1:05:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我们被击溃\N{\rEng}GXR, we're being overrun.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.01,1:06:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,基顿 不！\N{\rEng}Kitten, no!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.37,1:06:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 天哪\N{\rEng}Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.88,1:06:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 天哪 哦\N{\rEng}Oh, God! Oh! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.70,1:07:04.63,Chs,,0,0,0,,“联邦电视网”
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.13,1:07:08.77,Chs,,0,0,0,,“一小时内十万人丧命”
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.24,1:07:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,人类面临空前危机\N{\rEng}Crisis for humankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.99,1:07:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,舰队官员承认他们…\N{\rEng}Fleet officials admit they underestimated...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.41,1:07:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,低估虫族的防卫能力\N{\rEng}the Arachnids' defensive capability.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.92,1:07:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,因为克兰达夫星的惨剧\N{\rEng}Accepting responsibility for Klendathu...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.59,1:07:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,狄恩元帅引咎辞职\N{\rEng}Sky Marshal Dienes resigns.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.26,1:07:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,新任的元帅马休…\N{\rEng}His successor, Sky Marshal Tahat Meru...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.92,1:07:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,宣布她的战略\N{\rEng}outlines her new strategy.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.59,1:07:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须\N{\rEng}To fight the bug...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.60,1:07:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,了解虫族才能致胜\N{\rEng}we must understand the bug.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.10,1:07:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们绝对不能再重蹈克兰达夫的覆辙\N{\rEng}We can ill afford another Klendathu.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.97,1:07:41.62,Chs,,0,0,0,,你想知道更多吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.73,1:07:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,联邦科学家想…\N{\rEng}Federal scientists struggle to explain...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.90,1:07:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,解释虫族的军事智慧\N{\rEng}the intelligent military actions of the Arachnids.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.82,1:07:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,虫族经过三百代\N{\rEng}When a colony reaches a certain size...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.99,1:07:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,进化一定会变聪明\N{\rEng}300 generations or something, it gets smarter.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.78,1:07:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 聪明的虫子？ - 快…\N{\rEng}- Insects with intelligence? - Now, wait...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.24,1:07:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你遇到过吗？ 难以置信…\N{\rEng}Have you ever met one? I can't believe...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.08,1:07:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这种想法太荒谬了 - 请你听我说\N{\rEng}- I am hearing this nonsense. - Would you just wait a moment?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.08,1:08:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是我听过的最荒谬讲话 - 可能 可能\N{\rEng}- This is the most ridiculous conversation I have ever had. - Maybe... Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.12,1:08:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,也许有一种虫我们没见过\N{\rEng}there is some kind of bug that we haven't seen yet.:
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.92,1:08:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,领导阶级 虫族首脑\N{\rEng}a leadership caste, a-a hive brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.42,1:08:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,虫族首脑？ 虫子也会思考？ 才怪…\N{\rEng}Brain Bugs? Frankly, I find the idea of a bug that thinks offensive!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.11,1:08:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,星舰基地 杨罗杰号请求进入\N{\rEng}Ticonderoga, this is Rodger Young requesting approach vector.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.86,1:08:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,收到 杨罗杰号\N{\rEng}Affirmative, Rodger Young.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.78,1:08:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,座标l00951\N{\rEng}One-zero-zero-niner-five-two.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.66,1:08:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来\N{\rEng}Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.12,1:08:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\rEng}My God.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.37,1:08:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样？\N{\rEng}How could this happen?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.54,1:08:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们自以为比虫族聪明\N{\rEng}We thought we were smarter than the bugs.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.25,1:09:20.92,Chs,,0,0,0,,“伤亡人数：308 563”
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.08,1:09:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,很奇怪 几乎没有人被俘\N{\rEng}It's strange. There's almost no wounded at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.75,1:09:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,虫族不抓俘虏\N{\rEng}Bugs don't take prisoners.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.21,1:09:37.89,Chs,,0,0,0,,“强尼·瑞哥 阵亡”
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.89,1:09:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,哦…不…\N{\rEng}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.72,1:09:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,看\N{\rEng}Look.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.56,1:09:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 卡门… - 这里\N{\rEng}- Carmen... - See it? Right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.68,1:10:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他在那儿 - 我们会把他叫醒\N{\rEng}- There he is. - Come on, we'll just wake him up.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.52,1:10:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 强尼\N{\rEng}Hey,Johnny! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.02,1:10:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 瑞哥 - 强尼 醒醒\N{\rEng}- Hey, Rico! - Hey,Johnny!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.03,1:10:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 瑞哥 醒醒 - 你好吗 小鱼儿？\N{\rEng}- Hey, Rico!Wake up! - How you doin', fish boy?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.03,1:10:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,看 你死了\N{\rEng}Hey, look. You're dead!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.70,1:10:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你阵亡了\N{\rEng}Killed in action!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.37,1:10:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 再过三天就能出来 - 三天\N{\rEng}- Three more days. - Three days.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.37,1:10:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你出局了 - 再见\N{\rEng}- And you're out. - Good as new. See you later.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.46,1:10:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,回头见\N{\rEng}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.99,1:11:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,新的部队怎么样？\N{\rEng}So what do you hear about our new unit?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.82,1:11:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,硬汉部队消灭的大虫比谁都多\N{\rEng}Roughnecks killed more bugs than any other outfit on Big K.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.33,1:11:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,听说中尉很严厉\N{\rEng}Yeah, well, I hear their lieutenant's a real nutbuster.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.17,1:11:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,士官长是谁？\N{\rEng}Who's top kick?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.34,1:11:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你想当吗？\N{\rEng}You want the job, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.09,1:11:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我不介意\N{\rEng}I wouldn't mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.51,1:11:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我很介意\N{\rEng}I would.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.84,1:11:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想出力\N{\rEng}Just doing my part.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.26,1:11:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,命令\N{\rEng}Orders.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.35,1:11:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你的呢？\N{\rEng}Yours?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.85,1:11:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你还到哪里打过仗？\N{\rEng}Where you been besides Big K?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.68,1:11:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 土星外环 西格玛海滩 - 西格玛海滩\N{\rEng}- Outer rings, Zegema Beach. - Zegema Beach?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.65,1:11:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我一直想去那儿 - 好运气\N{\rEng}- I always wanted to go there. - Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.11,1:11:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不用去了 那里不存在了 - 听说你们的中尉挺麻烦的\N{\rEng}- It's not there any more. - So, I hear your lieutenant's a real nutbuster.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.28,1:11:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,别批评中尉 他救我一命\N{\rEng}No one talks about the lieutenant that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.12,1:11:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他救过我 - 也救过我\N{\rEng}- He saved my life. - Mine too.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.96,1:11:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我也是 - 还有我\N{\rEng}- Same for me. - Me too.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.63,1:12:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来他人很好\N{\rEng}Well, sounds like he's quite a guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.63,1:12:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为是谁救了你？\N{\rEng}Who do you think saved your ass?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.47,1:12:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,待命 立正\N{\rEng}Stand by. Attention on deck!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.31,1:12:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,新来的听好\N{\rEng}This is for you new people.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.48,1:12:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我只有一个规则\N{\rEng}I only have one rule:
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.61,1:12:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,全力以赴 不能退缩\N{\rEng}Everyone fights. No one quits.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.07,1:12:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,否则我们杀了你们 明白吗？\N{\rEng}You don't do your job, I'll shoot you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.16,1:12:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,明白吗？\N{\rEng}Do you get me?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.49,1:12:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,明白 长官\N{\rEng}We get you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.21,1:12:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 欢迎到硬汉部队 - 瑞斯加科的硬汉\N{\rEng}- Welcome to the Roughnecks. - Rasczak's Roughnecks!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.88,1:12:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,稍息 听好\N{\rEng}At ease. Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.04,1:12:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,新的元帅有新的战略\N{\rEng}We got a new Sky Marshal and a new battle plan.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.72,1:12:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,先一一消灭克兰达夫…\N{\rEng}We're gonna clean out the systems outlying Klendathu...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.22,1:12:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,周围的星球\N{\rEng}one planet at a time.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.47,1:12:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,明天攻击探戈幽灵星\N{\rEng}Tomorrow we hit Tango Urilla.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.72,1:12:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,先进行轰炸然后再消灭残留的敌人\N{\rEng}After Fleet glasses the planet, MI mops up.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.23,1:12:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,继续吧\N{\rEng}Carry on.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.74,1:13:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 分散开来\N{\rEng}All right. Spread out!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.41,1:13:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,核弹小组 找到虫穴就炸掉\N{\rEng}Fire teams! You locate a bug hole, nuke it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.92,1:14:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,华肯 带上弗洛斯和瑞哥\N{\rEng}Watkins, shake out Flores and Rico.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.92,1:14:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,收到 走吧\N{\rEng}Copy that. Move out!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.34,1:14:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,第一排 我们到山谷\N{\rEng}First platoon, we're going for that ridge.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.26,1:14:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 利维 跟我来 - 我要跟着瑞哥\N{\rEng}- Levy, you're with me. - No, I'm in A Squad. I'm going with Rico.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.26,1:14:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,给我闭嘴\N{\rEng}Shut up and follow me!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.18,1:14:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢那个？\N{\rEng}Hey, you like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.09,1:14:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,吃屎的大臭虫\N{\rEng}Fungus-sucking sack of maggot puke!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.18,1:14:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,华肯 它死了\N{\rEng}It's dead, Watkins! It's dead!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.89,1:15:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,死了就没什么可怕的\N{\rEng}Ain't much to look at after you scrape them off your boot.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.69,1:15:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,发现虫穴 那儿\N{\rEng}Bug hole. There.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.21,1:15:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,炸掉它 瑞哥\N{\rEng}Nuke 'em, Rico!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.38,1:15:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,准备射击\N{\rEng}Fire in the hole!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.56,1:15:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们受到攻击 快来支援\N{\rEng}Watkins, we're under heavy attack. Position M-4.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.06,1:15:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快去！ - 快！\N{\rEng}- Get over here! - Move!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.41,1:16:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你需要除虫吗 小姐？ - 闭嘴 大兵\N{\rEng}- You got a bug problem, ma'am? - Ah, stow it, trooper!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.98,1:16:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,大甲虫\N{\rEng}Tanker!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.14,1:16:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 妈的！ - 快走吧\N{\rEng}- Oh, shit! - Come on! Move!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.95,1:16:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,趴下来\N{\rEng}Get down!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.00,1:16:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我来\N{\rEng}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.53,1:18:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,通知救援队\N{\rEng}Stay down, sucker!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.70,1:18:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,呼叫检索\N{\rEng}Call for retrieval.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.37,1:18:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 医官 - 好身手\N{\rEng}- Medic! - Nice moves.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.54,1:18:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪儿学来的？\N{\rEng}Where'd you learn how to do that, soldier?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.87,1:18:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,学校里 你不记得吗？\N{\rEng}Back in school, sir. Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.04,1:18:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我是球队队长 - 瑞哥\N{\rEng}- I was captain of the team. - Rico?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.13,1:18:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 长官 - 我需要一名下士\N{\rEng}- Sir. - I need a corporal.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.97,1:18:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,在你阵亡之前你就当下士\N{\rEng}You're it until you're dead or till I find somebody better.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.47,1:18:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 长官\N{\rEng}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.56,1:18:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好了 结束了 - 干得好 下士\N{\rEng}- All right, saddle up! Show's over. - Way to go, Corporal.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.31,1:18:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我要一名班长 - 不行 找搞砸过\N{\rEng}- Hey, I need a squad leader. - Oh, no. No, I've been there and blew it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.73,1:18:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想杀敌\N{\rEng}I'm just here to fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.44,1:18:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢？\N{\rEng}What about it, Diz?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.69,1:18:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,看来就是我了\N{\rEng}Looks like I'm your girl, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.58,1:18:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 待会儿见 - 好\N{\rEng}- Catch you later. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.21,1:18:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,听好\N{\rEng}Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.17,1:19:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,最好的士兵要有最好的享受\N{\rEng}I expect the best, and I give the best!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.22,1:19:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这是啤酒\N{\rEng}Here's the beer!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.60,1:19:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这是娱乐的东西\N{\rEng}Here's the entertainment!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.06,1:19:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,玩得开心点 这是命今\N{\rEng}Have fun! That's an order!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.15,1:19:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的\N{\rEng}This one's for me!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.15,1:19:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了 中尉\N{\rEng}Thank you, Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.45,1:19:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞哥\N{\rEng}Rico!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.25,1:19:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你很会除虫\N{\rEng}You kill bugs good.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.41,1:19:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了\N{\rEng}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.58,1:19:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你在战前认识中尉了吧\N{\rEng}You knew the lieutenant before the war.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.00,1:19:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他为人如何？\N{\rEng}What was he like?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.01,1:19:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个老师 什么都懂\N{\rEng}He was a teacher. Kind of like he knew it all.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.18,1:19:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,总是带着微笑\N{\rEng}He always had this little smile.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.34,1:19:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他可笑不出来\N{\rEng}Yeah, well, he don't smile much any more.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.85,1:19:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,死这么多人怎么笑得出来\N{\rEng}Yeah, well, I guess your bottle fills up real quick when your kids get smeared.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.68,1:19:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 来吧 下士 - 我不跳舞了\N{\rEng}- Come on, Corporal. - Ah, nah, I don't do that any more.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.23,1:19:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得你以前跳 来嘛\N{\rEng}I remember when you used to dance. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.81,1:20:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我得下令吗？\N{\rEng}Do I have to pull rank?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.03,1:20:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 长官\N{\rEng}Excuse me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.37,1:20:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞哥 你问过我的意见 想听吗？\N{\rEng}Rico. You once asked me for advice. Want some now?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.54,1:20:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 想 长官 - 中尉 总部来电\N{\rEng}- Yes, sir. - Lieutenant, HQ is on the com.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.71,1:20:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,看到好机会就要把握\N{\rEng}Never pass up a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.73,1:20:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,华肯 喝啤酒吗？\N{\rEng}Watkins. Beer?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.88,1:21:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞哥 跳完舞你打算干嘛？\N{\rEng}So, Rico, what are you doing after the dance?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.09,1:21:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么好笑？\N{\rEng}What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.01,1:21:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,世事真是难以预料\N{\rEng}You know, just the way things work out.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.70,1:22:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们终于在一起\N{\rEng}We finally got together, Diz.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.37,1:22:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你 强尼\N{\rEng}I love you,Johnny.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.47,1:22:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞哥\N{\rEng}Rico!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.47,1:22:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,准备出动 欧文将军在P星遇难\N{\rEng}We're moving out. There's been a distress call from General Owen on Planet P.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.39,1:22:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,穿好军服 十分钟后报到\N{\rEng}So get your shit wired and report in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.64,1:22:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEng}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.14,1:22:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,谁在那里？\N{\rEng}Who's that with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.23,1:22:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,弗洛斯 长官\N{\rEng}Flores, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.49,1:22:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,二十分钟吧\N{\rEng}Make it 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.65,1:22:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 长官\N{\rEng}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.07,1:22:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,二十分钟？\N{\rEng}Twenty minutes?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.58,1:22:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,应该来得及\N{\rEng}We can do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.28,1:23:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,威士忌哨站 收到吗？\N{\rEng}Whiskey Outpost, do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.03,1:23:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这是硬汉部队201 请回答\N{\rEng}This is Roughneck 2-0 on tac three. Come in, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.37,1:23:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,威士忌哨站 威士忌哨站\N{\rEng}Whiskey Outpost, Whiskey Outpost,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.87,1:23:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这是硬汉部队201\N{\rEng}this is Roughneck 2-0 on tac three.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.21,1:23:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 将军有消息吗？ - 没有 长官\N{\rEng}- Any contact with General Owen? - No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.54,1:23:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,连发送讯号都没有\N{\rEng}Not even the transponder signal.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.05,1:23:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,被山谷挡住 到高处去\N{\rEng}It's these canyons. Go to higher ground, Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.43,1:24:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,威士忌哨站\N{\rEng}Whiskey Outpost, Whiskey Outpost...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.39,1:24:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这是硬汉部队\N{\rEng}this is Roughneck 2-0 on...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.32,1:24:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,把你的枪给我\N{\rEng}Sugar, your weapon.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.75,1:24:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我\N{\rEng}Help me! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.26,1:24:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我落入敌手 你们也要杀了我\N{\rEng}I'd expect anyone in this unit to do the same for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.22,1:24:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 瑞哥 - 长官\N{\rEng}- Rico. - Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.06,1:24:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你是代理士官长 带队\N{\rEng}You're acting sergeant. Move 'em out.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.44,1:24:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你们听到了 快走吧\N{\rEng}You heard the lieutenant! Saddle up!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.12,1:25:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪 有人血洗这地方\N{\rEng}Jeez, someone really humped the bunk.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.58,1:25:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 华肯 - 长官\N{\rEng}- Watkins. - Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.87,1:25:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,检查哨站 检查死尸\N{\rEng}Secure this compound. Police these bodies.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.29,1:25:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 长官 三个人上塔架 快点\N{\rEng}Yes, sir. Give me three up on the tower, now!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.54,1:25:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这里和那里建立监视哨\N{\rEng}Aye-aye.OP there! OP there!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.59,1:25:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,检查死尸\N{\rEng}Away! Number Two, police up these bodies!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.34,1:26:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,里头好臭\N{\rEng}Stinks in there.Second squad, come with me on the gate!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.38,1:26:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 瑞哥 - 是的 长官\N{\rEng}- Rico! - Churchill, come with me! - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.72,1:26:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要救援 这地方都是大虫\N{\rEng}We need retrieval. This place crawls.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.39,1:26:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,再找人修好通讯连线\N{\rEng}Get somebody in the communications tent and get me an uplink.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.72,1:26:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 长官 蒂丝 去吧\N{\rEng}Yes, sir. Diz, check it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.68,1:26:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 知道了 - 指挥小组跟我来\N{\rEng}- Roger. - Command group with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.73,1:26:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\rEng}Ah, shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.07,1:26:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,中尉\N{\rEng}Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.90,1:26:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他们吃饭时遭到大虫偷袭\N{\rEng}Dirty bugs came in right while they were having chow.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.75,1:26:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,它们从这里进来\N{\rEng}Yeah, this is where they got in.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.25,1:26:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,中尉\N{\rEng}Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.59,1:26:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好来看看\N{\rEng}I think you're gonna want to see this.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.38,1:26:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事 弗洛斯？\N{\rEng}What do you got, Flores?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.05,1:26:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这地方真可怕\N{\rEng}God, I hate this place.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.90,1:26:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得这是什么？ 瑞哥？\N{\rEng}What does that look like to you, Rico?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.07,1:27:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,看来虫钻进他大脑\N{\rEng}Looks like a bug was in his brain, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.75,1:27:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,它们吸光他大脑\N{\rEng}They sucked his brains out.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.76,1:27:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,打开来\N{\rEng}Open that.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.60,1:27:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,立正\N{\rEng}Officer on the deck!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.52,1:27:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 把将军扶起来 - 走了？\N{\rEng}- Pick up the general. - Gone?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.10,1:27:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,安全吗？ 我们得快走\N{\rEng}Is it safe? We've got to get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.77,1:27:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 将军 长官 - 我们…\N{\rEng}- General!, Sir! - We've gotta...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.44,1:27:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 谢谢你们\N{\rEng}Thank God for you, all of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.36,1:27:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都是英雄 你们全都是\N{\rEng}You're all gonna be heroes. Every last one of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.70,1:27:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 把洞穴封起来 - 好的\N{\rEng}- Close that hole. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.29,1:27:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我得逃命 联邦秘密太重要\N{\rEng}I had to evade capture. The security of the Federation was at stake.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.38,1:28:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这地区的攻击战略\N{\rEng}I have operational knowledge of what we're up to out here.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.21,1:28:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 赶快连线 - 我正在努力\N{\rEng}- Flores, I need that uplink. - Working on it, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.72,1:28:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你看\N{\rEng}Damn it.See?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.80,1:28:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,它们钻进你的大脑\N{\rEng}They get in your mind.Battlegroup, this is Roughneck 2-0.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.55,1:28:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你看法利的下场 - 你知道吗？\N{\rEng}- Look, they did it to Farley. - Do you read?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.22,1:28:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,它们钻进你的大脑 逼你做事情\N{\rEng}They got in his mind.Come in, Battlegroup. This is Roughneck 2-0.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.39,1:28:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,它们逼法利联络指挥部\N{\rEng}They make you do things. They made Farley call headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.56,1:28:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,求救讯号是个圈套\N{\rEng}The distress call was a trap.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.40,1:28:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,它们也想知道我们的底细\N{\rEng}They're just like us. They want to know what makes us tick.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.86,1:28:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,摸清我们的弱点 这样才能消灭我们\N{\rEng}They want to know us, so they can kill us.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.90,1:28:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人会来袭 准备迎战\N{\rEng}Roughnecks, this is lead. Prepare for attack.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.90,1:28:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们会被攻击 - 救援机在哪呢？\N{\rEng}- I repeat, we're gonna be attacked. - Where's the retrieval boat?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.32,1:28:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,紧急状况这是硬汉部队 收到吗？\N{\rEng}Mayday. Mayday. This is Roughneck 2-0 to Battlegroup. Do you read?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.33,1:28:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 天哪\N{\rEng}Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.24,1:28:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪 我们死定了 懂吗？\N{\rEng}We're gonna die! Don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.25,1:28:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都要死了\N{\rEng}We're all gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.17,1:28:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,第二阵容 跟我来！\N{\rEng}Second squad, follow me!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.67,1:28:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 克制一下自己 将军 - 不行\N{\rEng}- Control yourself, General. - I can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.71,1:28:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我不行 我做不到\N{\rEng}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.34,1:28:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你干脆杀死我\N{\rEng}I wish you'd just shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.34,1:28:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,中尉 他的脑袋不清楚\N{\rEng}Lieutenant! He's just a little out of his mind, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.01,1:28:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,大虫\N{\rEng}Bugs! Bugs!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.02,1:28:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEng}Die! All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.35,1:29:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好 全力开火\N{\rEng}Warm it all up! Everything you've got!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.36,1:29:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快 - 大兵们 拚命吧\N{\rEng}- Move! - Come on, you apes!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.52,1:29:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你们想一直活着吧？\N{\rEng}You want to live forever?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.40,1:29:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这儿！ - 我这边有虫子！\N{\rEng}- Here! - I got bugs!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.18,1:29:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,开火吧\N{\rEng}Fire at will!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.93,1:30:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,飞虫来袭\N{\rEng}Incoming!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.39,1:30:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞哥 连线好了吗？\N{\rEng}Rico, where's my communication?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.68,1:30:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 蒂丝 连线呢？ - 再等一分钟\N{\rEng}- Diz, status on the uplink! - Give me a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.85,1:30:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有一分钟了\N{\rEng}We don't have a minute!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.03,1:31:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,舰队 这是硬汉部队\N{\rEng}Battlegroup, this is Roughneck 2-0. We are under...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.19,1:31:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这里是杨罗杰号 请说 - 我们受袭 请来救援\N{\rEng}- This is Rodger Young. Go ahead. - We are under attack, sir. We need retrieval now!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.36,1:31:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,P星球没敌人\N{\rEng}We have Planet Pas clear.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.87,1:31:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,到处都是 快来接人\N{\rEng}This place crawls, sir. We need pickup now!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.03,1:31:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 说出位置 - 追踪无线电讯号\N{\rEng}- What's your position? - Come down on this transmission.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.37,1:31:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,哨站？ 太疯狂了\N{\rEng}Inside the outpost? That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.04,1:31:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,希望飞行员也疯狂 完毕\N{\rEng}Well, I hope you have a crazy pilot. Out!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.49,1:31:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,中尉\N{\rEng}Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.20,1:31:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,救援机正赶来\N{\rEng}Boat coming down, sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.87,1:32:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,退进去 快撤\N{\rEng}Fall back into the compound! Fall back!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.06,1:32:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,全力抵挡敌人\N{\rEng}Hold here! Hold what you've got!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.41,1:32:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,弹药快没了\N{\rEng}Running low!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.08,1:32:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我没了\N{\rEng}I'm out!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.58,1:32:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,拿去 省着点\N{\rEng}Here! Make 'em count!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.27,1:33:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,掩护救援机 撤\N{\rEng}Make cover fire! Fall back!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.29,1:33:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快 快 快\N{\rEng}Move, move, move!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.46,1:33:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,快登机 撤\N{\rEng}Fall back to the boat! Haul ass!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.68,1:33:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我的天 - 哦\N{\rEng}- Oh, my God! - Oh!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.40,1:33:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 把他拉上来 - 快\N{\rEng}- Get him outta there! Pull! - Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.16,1:34:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞哥 瑞哥\N{\rEng}Rico! Rico!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.66,1:34:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你知道该怎么做 - 是的 长官\N{\rEng}- You know what to do! - Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.67,1:34:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,快下手 瑞哥\N{\rEng}Do it, Rico!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.53,1:34:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗯！ - 蒂丝！\N{\rEng}- Yeah! - Dizzy!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.97,1:35:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\N{\rEng}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.80,1:35:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,王牌 帮我拉住她\N{\rEng}Ace, help me! Hold her down!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.56,1:35:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,把她抬上机\N{\rEng}Move! Get her into the boat!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.31,1:35:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂丝 千万别死\N{\rEng}Come on, Diz! Don't die on me!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.19,1:35:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,把她抬走 快\N{\rEng}Let's get her out! Let's go, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.91,1:35:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,快上去\N{\rEng}Let's go! Get aboard!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.24,1:35:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你们 快点…\N{\rEng}Tower, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.25,1:35:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,快来吧\N{\rEng}Let's move it, tower! Run!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.22,1:35:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,升空\N{\rEng}Lift off!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.21,1:36:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 强尼 我快死了 - 不\N{\rEng}- Johnny, I'm dying-dying. - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.76,1:36:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不 你不会有事的 蒂丝\N{\rEng}You're gonna be all right, Diz.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.01,1:36:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系\N{\rEng}It's all right...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.26,1:36:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我爱过你\N{\rEng}because I got to have you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.19,1:36:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,别放开我\N{\rEng}Johnny, don't let me go!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.32,1:36:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,强…强…\N{\rEng}Joh...Joh...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.15,1:36:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,别放开…别放开…\N{\rEng}Don't let... Don't let...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.72,1:37:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你知道\N{\rEng}I think you should know...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.68,1:37:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你的朋友瑞哥在后面\N{\rEng}your friend Rico is back there.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.23,1:37:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,快通知舰队轰炸这星球\N{\rEng}Get on the com and tell Fleet to glass that rock.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.07,1:37:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,谁下的命令 下士？\N{\rEng}On whose authority, Corporal?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.86,1:37:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我的命令 任务由我指挥\N{\rEng}That would be mine, sir. I assumed command of the mission.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.37,1:37:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,杨罗杰号 我正式代表\N{\rEng}Rodger Young, we have an official request...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.91,1:37:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,机动部队要求轰炸P星球\N{\rEng}by the Mobile Infantry to commence bombardment of Planet P.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.38,1:37:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你死了\N{\rEng}I thought you were dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.88,1:37:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我没死 很多战友都死了\N{\rEng}I'm not, but a lot of my troopers are.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.05,1:37:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\rEng}Negative on your request, DeRuyter.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.09,1:37:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,元帅另有安排\N{\rEng}The Sky Marshal has other plans for Planet P.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.39,1:37:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来\N{\rEng}Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.72,1:37:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,机动部队负责死 舰队负责飞\N{\rEng}MI does the dying. Fleet just does the flying.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.89,1:37:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 有动静了\N{\rEng}Hold on. Something's up.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.89,1:38:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,舰队要进行大规模行动\N{\rEng}Fleet's mobilized for a big operation.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.20,1:38:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,立正\N{\rEng}Attention on deck!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.12,1:38:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,有人曾问我…\N{\rEng}Once somebody asked me...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.12,1:38:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,公民和平民…\N{\rEng}if I knew the difference between a citizen...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.63,1:38:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,有何不同\N{\rEng}and a civilian.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.63,1:38:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在知道了\N{\rEng}I can tell you now.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.30,1:38:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,公民有…\N{\rEng}A citizen has the courage...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.47,1:38:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,捍卫人类安全的勇气\N{\rEng}to make the safety of the human race their personal responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.14,1:38:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂丝是我朋友\N{\rEng}Dizzy was my friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.64,1:39:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,她也是战士\N{\rEng}She was a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.85,1:39:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,更重要的是\N{\rEng}But more than that...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.81,1:39:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,她是联邦公民\N{\rEng}she was a citizen of the Federation.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.65,1:39:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,敬礼\N{\rEng}Present arms!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.09,1:39:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,放下\N{\rEng}Order arms!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.26,1:39:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,向左转\N{\rEng}Left face!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.11,1:39:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 立正 - 继续\N{\rEng}- Officer on deck! - Carry on.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.78,1:39:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,治葬队伍解散\N{\rEng}Burial detail dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.46,1:40:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,稍息\N{\rEng}At ease.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.79,1:40:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好吗 卡尔？ - 我很好 卡门\N{\rEng}- How are you, Carl? - Carmen, good.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.13,1:40:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,强尼 我很遗憾你们被派到P星球\N{\rEng}Johnny, I'm sorry it had to be your unit on P.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.13,1:40:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那次任务的生还率很低\N{\rEng}That mission had a very low survival probability.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.68,1:40:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,虫族设下圈套 对吧？\N{\rEng}The bugs laid a trap for us, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.14,1:40:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,证明它们有智慧\N{\rEng}Elegant proof of intelligence, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.64,1:40:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我早就猜到P星球上有虫族首脑\N{\rEng}We thought there might be a Brain Bug on P.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.19,1:40:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你早就知道却派他们下去？\N{\rEng}You knew, and you sent them anyway?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.19,1:40:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们找不到首脑就不能进行攻击\N{\rEng}We couldn't afford to launch an operation if there wasn't one.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.48,1:40:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你不苟同 很遗憾\N{\rEng}You don't approve. Well, too bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.99,1:40:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,事关人类存亡\N{\rEng}We're in this for the species, boys and girls.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.99,1:40:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,它们数量众多\N{\rEng}It's simple numbers. They have more.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.45,1:40:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我每天都得决定…\N{\rEng}And every day I have to make decisions...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.29,1:40:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,派你这种人去送死\N{\rEng}that send hundreds of people like you to their deaths.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.21,1:40:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你不知道吗 中校？\N{\rEng}Didn't they tell you, Colonel?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.67,1:40:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,机动部队专门送死\N{\rEng}That's what the Mobile Infantry is good for.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.09,1:40:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你还能再战\N{\rEng}I hope you're ready for more.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.96,1:40:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要回去活抓首脑\N{\rEng}We're going back to P to capture that Brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.30,1:41:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,硬汉部队随时备战\N{\rEng}The Roughnecks are always ready, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.14,1:41:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他们需要一名中尉 想当吗？\N{\rEng}I hear they need a new lieutenant. Want the job?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.85,1:41:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 等我阵亡你再换人\N{\rEng}I'll take it, till I get killed or you find someone better.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.06,1:41:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,全体人员报到\N{\rEng}Attention. All personnel report to your stations.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.32,1:41:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,75分钟后降落\N{\rEng}- Well... - Prepare for drop in 7 5 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.82,1:41:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你要小心 强尼\N{\rEng}Take care of yourself,Johnny.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.70,1:41:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,后会有期\N{\rEng}I'll see you again.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.67,1:41:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,立正\N{\rEng}Officer on deck!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.77,1:41:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这些孩子是谁？ - 支援部队\N{\rEng}- Who are all these kids? - We got reinforced.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.44,1:41:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,多半是菜鸟\N{\rEng}Most of them are fresh out of boot.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.74,1:41:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们算是老兵\N{\rEng}We're the old men, Ace.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.95,1:42:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,新兵听好\N{\rEng}This is for all you new people.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.29,1:42:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我只有一个规则\N{\rEng}I only have one rule:
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.62,1:42:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,全力以赴 不能退缩\N{\rEng}Everyone fights. No one quits.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:09.79,1:42:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不尽力我就亲自宰了你\N{\rEng}If you don't do your job, I'll kill you myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.96,1:42:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,明白吗？\N{\rEng}Do you get me?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.34,1:42:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,明白 长官\N{\rEng}We get you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.46,1:42:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 欢迎加入硬汉部队 - 瑞哥的硬汉部队\N{\rEng}- Welcome to the Roughnecks. - Rico's Roughnecks!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.76,1:42:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,今天要进入虫穴\N{\rEng}Today we're gonna pay a visit to Bug City.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.43,1:42:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,找一只没见过的大虫\N{\rEng}We're lookin' for a bug no one's ever seen before.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.81,1:42:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,一只聪明的虫子\N{\rEng}Some kind of smart bug.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.57,1:42:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,它可能知道我们要去 来吧\N{\rEng}And it probably knows we're comin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.62,1:42:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,快！ 跑 跑 跑\N{\rEng}Come on! Run, run, run, run, run!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.96,1:42:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,快闪躲\N{\rEng}Evasive action.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.28,1:43:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,准备进行超光速飞行\N{\rEng}Get us clear for warp, Number Two.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.16,1:43:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,五秒后 四…三…\N{\rEng}Clear in five, four...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:26.66,1:43:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 开始转换超光速引擎… - 三…五\N{\rEng}- Initiating star drive... - three...in five.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.81,1:43:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,杨罗杰号被击中 就快坠毁\N{\rEng}This is Rodger Young. We're going down Repeat, this is Rodger Young.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.31,1:43:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快离开这里 - 弃舰…\N{\rEng}- Get out! We're going down. - Abandon ship! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.15,1:44:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,卡门！\N{\rEng}Carmen! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.32,1:44:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 山德！ - 这！\N{\rEng}- Zander! - Here!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.16,1:44:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快赶去逃生艇 - 来吧\N{\rEng}- We've got to get to the rescue deck! - Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:24.84,1:44:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长\N{\rEng}Captain!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.18,1:44:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,快弃舰 这是命…\N{\rEng}Abandon ship. That's an...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.52,1:44:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,她死了 卡门 她死了\N{\rEng}She's dead, Carmen. She's dead!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.46,1:44:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿\N{\rEng}Go! Here!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:11.72,1:45:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我来\N{\rEng}Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.82,1:45:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好了吗？\N{\rEng}Ready?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.43,1:45:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,B63逃生艇 两人在艇上\N{\rEng}Life pod Bravo 6-3, two aboard.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.86,1:46:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,搜寻降落点 扫瞄地形 这儿\N{\rEng}Scanning for a landing zone! Checking terrain. Here!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.61,1:46:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你行吗？ - 小意思\N{\rEng}- Can you handle that? - Piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.49,1:46:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们失去了杨罗杰号 - 你们在什么位置？\N{\rEng}- We've lost the Rodger Young! - What is your position?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.12,1:46:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,经过确实 杨罗杰号坠毁\N{\rEng}Flight Command, we have confirmation. The Rodger Young is down.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:18.79,1:46:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,强尼\N{\rEng}Oh.Johnny!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.79,1:46:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,强尼\N{\rEng}Johnny!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.46,1:46:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,杨罗杰号遭击毁\N{\rEng}Rodger Young just burned up.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.51,1:46:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,在救援\N{\rEng}It's on the rescue net.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.97,1:46:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有生还者？\N{\rEng}Any survivors?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.97,1:46:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,情况很糟\N{\rEng}Well, they're getting tarred up there pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.68,1:46:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,B63逃生艇\N{\rEng}Bravo 6-3, two aboard.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.14,1:46:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,收到吗？\N{\rEng}Is anyone receiving?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:40.81,1:46:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有人收到吗？ - 收到\N{\rEng}- Is anyone receiving? - Affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.27,1:46:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是硬汉部队\N{\rEng}This is Roughneck 2-0.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.86,1:46:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,讯号中断 请重覆\N{\rEng}You're breaking up. Say again.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.48,1:46:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 卡门？ - 请重复 信号中断\N{\rEng}- Carmen? - Say again. I'm losing you.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.94,1:46:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,卡门！\N{\rEng}Carmen!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.20,1:46:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,准备降落\N{\rEng}Prepare for landing.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.66,1:46:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,反向推动器 三…\N{\rEng}Retros in three...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.58,1:46:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,二…一…启动\N{\rEng}two, one, fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.14,1:47:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,卡门 卡门\N{\rEng}Carmen. Carmen.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.02,1:47:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你没事吧？ - 嗯\N{\rEng}- Hey, are you okay? - Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.27,1:47:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,快下来\N{\rEng}Get out. Get out.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.32,1:47:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这是硬汉部队 收到吗？\N{\rEng}This is Roughneck 2-0. Are you receiving? Over. This is Roughneck 2-0.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.53,1:47:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 卡门 你收到吗？ - 强尼 是你吗？\N{\rEng}- Carmen, are you receiving? - Johnny, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.08,1:47:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是我 你的位置和状况如何？\N{\rEng}It's me! Wh, what's your position and situation?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.87,1:47:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在虫穴 地下二十米\N{\rEng}We're in Bug City, 20 metres underground.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.58,1:47:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,位置是…南42 东118\N{\rEng}Position: south 42, east 118.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.92,1:47:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,状况…\N{\rEng}Situation is...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.05,1:47:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,重复 南42 东118\N{\rEng}I repeat. South 4 2, east 118.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.92,1:47:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,状况呢？\N{\rEng}What's your situation? Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:52.43,1:47:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,卡门\N{\rEng}Carmen.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:56.05,1:47:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,状况很危险\N{\rEng}Situation is extremely hostile.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.89,1:48:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,快派小队救援\N{\rEng}I need a squad to pull 'em out!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.94,1:48:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 方向？ - 西南方三公里\N{\rEng}- Direction? - Three clicks, south by southwest.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.61,1:48:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,小心\N{\rEng}Look out!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.26,1:48:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么办？ - 大伙听到了\N{\rEng}- What do you wanna do? - You heard the lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.85,1:48:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,救援队 第三班跟我来\N{\rEng}Rescue party! Third squad, come with me!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:41.27,1:48:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,取消命令\N{\rEng}Cancel that!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:43.77,1:48:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都知道她已经死了\N{\rEng}You know as well as I do, she's already dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.94,1:48:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,很遗憾 老兄\N{\rEng}Sorry, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:53.28,1:48:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,硬汉部队 前进\N{\rEng}Roughnecks, let's move.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.95,1:48:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rEng}All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.80,1:49:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,它们为何不杀死我们？\N{\rEng}Why didn't they kill us?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.80,1:49:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,它们要活捉我们\N{\rEng}They want us alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:11.94,1:50:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们应该走这边\N{\rEng}We should go this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:15.61,1:50:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A连前往这方向\N{\rEng}A Company's that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:18.11,1:50:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 可是卡门在这儿\N{\rEng}Yeah, but Carmen's down there.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:22.45,1:50:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,恕我直言 老兄 她已经死了\N{\rEng}Hey, I hate to be rude, buddy, but word has it she's dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:27.29,1:50:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,她还活着\N{\rEng}She's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.62,1:50:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道？\N{\rEng}How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.96,1:50:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别问我 我就是知道 - 听着\N{\rEng}- I don't know how I know, but I know. - Listen.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:33.75,1:50:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,指挥官违反命令的…\N{\rEng}You got command, but going off mission...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.26,1:50:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,罪名很重\N{\rEng}That's a serious offence.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.72,1:50:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你会被判吊刑\N{\rEng}I think they hang you for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:42.89,1:50:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,硬汉20部队继续前进\N{\rEng}Roughneck 2-0, proceed on mission.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.81,1:50:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我要两名自愿者\N{\rEng}I need two volunteers.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.26,1:52:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,有一天\N{\rEng}One day...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:01.84,1:52:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,像我这样的人…\N{\rEng}someone like me...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:04.34,1:52:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,会消灭你们…\N{\rEng}is gonna kill you...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:06.18,1:52:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,整个臭虫族\N{\rEng}and your whole fucking race.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:07.37,1:53:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道这是什么吗？\N{\rEng}You know what this is?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.54,1:53:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你当然知道\N{\rEng}Sure you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.46,1:53:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你是肥大的聪明虫\N{\rEng}You're some kind of big, fat, smart bug...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:17.13,1:53:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧？\N{\rEng}aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.67,1:53:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\rEng}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:34.06,1:53:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这是硬汉部队\N{\rEng}This is Roughneck 2-0.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:35.94,1:53:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,虫族首脑往西五区前进\N{\rEng}Brain Bug sighted moving west of grid five.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:41.82,1:53:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,快跑\N{\rEng}Run!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:13.35,1:54:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,快 快\N{\rEng}Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:15.89,1:54:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 核弹给我 - 你想当英雄吗？\N{\rEng}- Give me the nuke! - You trying to be a hero, Watkins?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:21.52,1:54:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要除虫\N{\rEng}I'm trying to kill some bugs, sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:24.99,1:54:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你们快走\N{\rEng}Get outta here! Get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:29.70,1:54:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快走吧\N{\rEng}Move!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:35.70,1:54:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊 想死吗\N{\rEng}Come on! You like that? You like that? Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:39.04,1:54:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,想死吗？ 吃子弹吧\N{\rEng}You want a little more?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:43.80,1:54:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,想死吗？ 吃子弹吧\N{\rEng}You like that? You like that? You like that? You like that? You want a little more?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:53.10,1:54:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,来呀 来呀\N{\rEng}Come on! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:59.64,1:55:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\rEng}Come on, come on, come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:25.50,1:55:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 卡门\N{\rEng}Come on, Carmen.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:39.02,1:55:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们成功了！\N{\rEng}We did it! We won!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:46.86,1:55:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么回事？ - 逮到它了\N{\rEng}- What's going on? - They got it!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:49.19,1:55:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,来呀\N{\rEng}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:33.66,1:56:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,它在想什么 中校？\N{\rEng}What's it thinking, Colonel?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:53.97,1:56:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,它很害怕\N{\rEng}It's afraid.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:56.73,1:56:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,怕得要命\N{\rEng}It's afraid!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:02.11,1:57:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快 - 好！\N{\rEng}- Come on. - Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:05.57,1:57:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,卡尔！ 卡尔！\N{\rEng}Carl! Carl! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:07.99,1:57:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你们还活着 很好\N{\rEng}Well, look who's here. You made it. Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:10.99,1:57:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你教我的 是你教我去找卡门\N{\rEng}It was you, wasn't it? You told me how to find Carmen.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:14.39,1:57:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这是机密\N{\rEng}Well, that's classified.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:17.92,1:57:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们三个在一起就…\N{\rEng}You know, whenever the three of us are together...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:20.75,1:57:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,能无往不胜\N{\rEng}I feel like things might just work out.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:23.76,1:57:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你说的对 卡门\N{\rEng}I hope you're right, Carmen.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:25.76,1:57:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们逮到虫族首脑 很快就知道它们的弱点\N{\rEng}We've got one of their Brains now. Pretty soon we'll know how they think.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:28.76,1:57:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一来就能击败它们\N{\rEng}And then we'll know how to beat them.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:31.43,1:57:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,有一天战争会结束\N{\rEng}One day it will all be over...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:33.60,1:57:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,大家会忘记这场奋战的功臣\N{\rEng}and everyone will forget that this was the moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:36.60,1:57:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,回想之时\N{\rEng}This is when it turned.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:39.60,1:57:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不是强大的舰队或是犀利的武器\N{\rEng}And it wasn't the mighty Fleet, it wasn't some fancy new weapon.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:47.61,1:57:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,而是逮到虫族首脑的辛姆教官\N{\rEng}It was a drill instructor named Zim who captured a Brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:52.45,1:57:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好 - 辛姆？\N{\rEng}- Yeah! - Zim?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:58.42,1:58:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,辛姆逮到大虫\N{\rEng}Zim. Zim got the bug.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:00.75,1:58:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,辛姆逮到大虫\N{\rEng}Zim got the bug, man!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:02.42,1:58:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 干得好 中士 - 谢谢你 长官\N{\rEng}- Good job, Sergeant. - Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:05.80,1:58:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我是二等兵 - 继续 二等兵\N{\rEng}- That would be private, sir. - Carry on, Private.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:10.72,1:58:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的 长官 - 好\N{\rEng}- Yes, sir! - Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:17.77,1:58:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,虫族首脑将透露什么秘密？\N{\rEng}What mysteries will the Brain Bug reveal?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:20.94,1:58:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,科学家日以继夜 探索它的奥秘\N{\rEng}Federal scientists are working around the clock to probe its secrets.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:25.94,1:58:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦了解虫族就能消灭它们\N{\rEng}Once we understand the bug, we will defeat it.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:35.62,1:58:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有舰队\N{\rEng}We have the ships.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:37.21,1:58:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有武器\N{\rEng}We have the weapons.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:40.04,1:58:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要战士\N{\rEng}We need soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:42.13,1:58:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,像丝黛克中尉这种战士\N{\rEng}Soldiers like Lieutenant Stack Lumbrezer.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:44.46,1:58:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,抵达目标区 舰长\N{\rEng}We're over the target area now, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:46.63,1:58:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还有卡门·艾邦妮兹舰长 - 我是舰长\N{\rEng}- And Captain Carmen Ibanez. - This is the captain speaking.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:49.89,1:58:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,准备降落\N{\rEng}All personnel prepare for drop.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:51.64,1:58:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,二等兵利维和瑞哥中尉\N{\rEng}Soldiers like Private Ace Levy and Lieutenant John Rico.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:54.47,1:58:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,大兵们 拚命吧\N{\rEng}Come on, you apes! You wanna live forever?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:58.06,1:58:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要你\N{\rEng}We need you all.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:59.60,1:59:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,服役就有公民权\N{\rEng}Service guarantees citizenship.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:09.66,1:59:12.49,Chs,,0,0,0,,“继续奋战”
Dialogue: 0,1:59:13.80,1:59:16.55,Chs,,0,0,0,,“胜利在望”
